nsider.com%2Frfk-jr-claims-unconstitutional-to-make-him-say-where-lives-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERobert%20F.%20Kennedy%20Jr.%3C%2Fa%3E%20stowed%20the%20bear%20carcass%20in%20the%20back%20of%20his%20car%2C%20he%20said.%20He%20spent%20the%20day%20hunting%20with%20hawks%20and%20got%20dinner%20with%20friends%20at%20a%20Peter%20Luger%20steakhouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDay%20turned%20to%20dusk.%20Kennedy%20needed%20to%20catch%20a%20flight.%20He%20realized%20he%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20skin%20the%20bear%20and%20put%20its%20flesh%20into%20his%20refrigerator%20in%20his%20Westchester%20home%20in%20time.%20So%20he%20stashed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobert-kennedy-dumped-dead-bear-cub-central-park-new-york-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebear%20cub%20carcass%20in%20Central%20Park%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20he%20thought%20would%20be%20funny%2C%20he%20recounted%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20some%20point%20during%20that%20day%2C%20Kennedy%20%E2%80%94%20who%20is%20now%20an%20independent%20candidate%20for%20president%20of%20the%20United%20States%20%E2%80%94%20posed%20with%20the%20bear%20cub's%20corpse%20in%20a%20photo%20that%20became%20instantly%20famous%20when%20the%20New%20Yorker%20published%20it%20earlier%20this%20month.%20He%20stuck%20his%20hand%20in%20the%20bear's%20bloody%20mouth%2C%20looked%20down%2C%20and%20grimaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20turns%20out%2C%20Kennedy%20may%20have%20been%20touching%20the%20bear's%20brain%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20obtained%20the%20state%20report%20detailing%20the%20necropsy%20the%20Department%20of%20Environmental%20Conservation%20performed%20on%20the%20bear%20cub.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20document%20reveals%20Kennedy%20had%20good%20instincts%20when%20it%20came%20to%20evaluating%20the%20bear's%20flesh.%20The%20animal%20%26quot%3Bis%20in%20good%20flesh%20with%20good%20fat%20reserves%20for%20its%20age%20and%20season%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Do5ECFLG2EwI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKevin%20Hynes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20wildlife%20biologist%20who%20performed%20the%20necropsy%2C%20wrote%20in%20his%20report%20for%20the%20department's%20Wildlife%20Health%20Unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20carcass%20is%20relatively%20fresh%20and%20the%20tissues%20are%20in%20good%20postmortem%20condition%2C%26quot%3B%20Hynes%20wrote%20in%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%207-%20or%208-month-old%20female%20bear%20was%20smashed%20in%20the%20head%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20consistent%20with%20Kennedy's%20story%20that%20it%20was%20hit%20by%20a%20van.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cranium%20was%20%26quot%3Bdestroyed%2C%26quot%3B%20Hynes%20wrote%2C%20and%20the%20brain%20tissue%20left%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bscrambled%2C%20liquefied%2C%20and%20hemorrhagic.%26quot%3B%20Much%20of%20the%20bear's%20brain%20tissue%20leaked%20and%20exited%20through%20its%20mouth%20and%20nostrils%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20brain%20structures%20are%20unrecognizable%20(unsuitable%20for%20rabies%20testing)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReached%20by%20phone%2C%20Hynes%20referred%20questions%20to%20the%20New%20York%20Department%20of%20Environmental%20Conservation%2C%20which%20declined%20to%20make%20him%20available%20for%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newyorker.com%2Fmagazine%2F2024%2F08%2F12%2Frobert-f-kennedy-jr-profile-presidential-campaign%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%20with%20the%20New%20Yorker%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Kennedy%20speculated%20that%20sticking%20his%20hand%20in%20the%20bear's%20mouth%20may%20be%20how%20he%20got%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frfk-jr-brain-dead-worm-parasite-expert-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebrain%20worm.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20testified%20about%20the%20parasite%20in%20his%20own%20cranium%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%20a%20deposition%20two%20years%20before%20the%20bear%20was%20killed%2C%20according%20to%20The%20New%20York%20Times.%20In%20the%20deposition%2C%20Kennedy%20said%20a%20doctor%20told%20him%20the%20worm%20went%20%26quot%3Binto%20my%20brain%20and%20ate%20a%20portion%20of%20it%20and%20then%20died.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Kennedy's%20presidential%20campaign%20didn't%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bear's%20skin%2C%20carcass%2C%20and%20brain%20tissue%20sample%20were%20frozen%20and%20locked%20away%20in%20the%20state%20environmental%20department's%20wildlife%20health%20unit.%20The%20frozen%20remains%20are%20no%20longer%20in%20the%20department's%20possession%2C%20according%20to%20agency%20spokesperson%20Jeff%20Wernick%2C%20who%20said%20samples%20%26quot%3Bgenerally%20get%20destroyed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e9ea8d17-8711-4c7a-9623-e4c63b92e297%5C%22%3ERFK%20Jr.%20and%20the%20bear%20carcass%20may%20have%20something%20else%20in%20common%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKennedy%20first%20disclosed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobert-kennedy-dumped-dead-bear-cub-central-park-new-york-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebear%20story%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%20a%20video%20posted%20to%20social%20media%20ahead%20of%20the%20publication%20of%20the%20New%20Yorker%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20said%2C%20'Let's%20go%20put%20the%20bear%20in%20Central%20Park%2C%20and%20we'll%20make%20it%20look%20like%20he%20got%20hit%20by%20a%20bike%2C'%26quot%3B%20Kennedy%20said%20in%20the%20video.%20%26quot%3BIt'll%20be%20fun%2C%20funny%20for%20people.%20So%20everybody%20thought%2C%20'That's%20a%20great%20idea.'%20So%20we%20went%20and%20did%20that%2C%20and%20we%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20amusing%20for%20whoever%20found%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20walking%20her%20dog%20found%20the%20bear%20the%20next%20day%2C%20October%206%2C%20around%208%3A45%20a.m.%20Law%20enforcement%20organizations%20moved%20the%20carcass%20from%20underneath%20a%20bicycle%2C%20which%20Kennedy%20or%20one%20of%20his%20friends%20apparently%20left%20on%20top%20of%20it%2C%20wrapped%20it%20in%20a%20tarp%2C%20and%20took%20it%20to%20the%20Wildlife%20Health%20Unit%20for%20the%20necropsy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHynes%2C%20examining%20the%20bear's%20corpse%2C%20quickly%20concluded%20that%20the%20cub%20was%20likely%20killed%20by%20a%20vehicle.%20Until%20RFK%20publicly%20took%20credit%20for%20dumping%20the%20bear's%20corpse%2C%20authorities%20had%20no%20idea%20who%20put%20it%20there.%20The%20DEC%20records%20indicate%20the%20case%20was%20closed%20by%20the%20end%20of%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Robert%20Kennedy%20Jr.%20at%20a%20microphone%2C%20pointing%20up.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bf94611aa2ac29ee31f333%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERobert%20F.%20Kennedy%20Jr.%20is%20running%20as%20an%20independent%20candidate%20in%20the%202024%20presidential%20election.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FEduardo%20Munoz%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKennedy's%20revelation%20that%20he%20was%20involved%20in%20moving%20the%20bear's%20corpse%20came%20too%20late%20for%20any%20law%20enforcement%20action%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Eover%20his%20possession%20or%20disposal%20of%20the%20corpse%2C%20said%20Wernick%2C%20of%20the%20environmental%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20statute%20of%20limitations%20for%20these%20offenses%20is%20one%20year%3B%20charges%20cannot%20be%20brought%20for%20incidents%20that%20occurred%20more%20than%20one%20year%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20Wernick%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20the%20roadkill%20incident%2C%20the%20bear%20cub%20and%20Kennedy%20may%20have%20something%20else%20in%20common%3