ppearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20billowy%2C%20soft%20couches%20look%20like%20the%20perfect%20place%20to%20sink%20into%20and%20relax%20after%20a%20long%20day%2C%20but%20in%20reality%2C%20I%20think%20they%20lack%20proper%20support.%20Plus%20they%20don't%20always%20hold%20their%20shape%20%E2%80%94%20down-feather-filled%20cushions%20can%20compress%20after%20being%20sat%20on%20too%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBehind%20every%20cloud-style%20sofa%20featured%20on%20social%20media%2C%20there's%20probably%20an%20influencer%20picking%20up%20the%20surprisingly%20heavy%20cushions%20and%20shaking%20them%20out%20to%20restore%20their%20shape%20right%20before%20they%20press%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20investing%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-buy-for-living-room-interior-designers-worth-it-2022-6%5C%22%3Ehigh-end%20sofa%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20look%20for%20something%20that%20will%20more%20likely%20hold%20up%20over%20time.%20I%20recommend%20going%20for%20cushions%20filled%20with%20high-resilient-density%20foam%20instead.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhite%20outdoor%20cushions%20look%20clean%20and%20crisp%20%E2%80%A6%20for%20about%20one%20day.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22white%20outdoor%20furniture%20cushions%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63ee5c7369b9cb001880b4bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20outdoor%20furniture%2C%20you%20may%20want%20to%20avoid%20white%20fabrics.%3Cp%3EArina%20P%20Habich%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhite%20outdoor%20cushions%20are%20a%20popular%20choice%20for%20their%20timeless%20and%20elegant%20look.%20But%2C%20as%20any%20homeowners%20with%20white%20cushions%20can%20attest%2C%20the%20reality%20of%20owning%20them%20is%20far%20from%20ideal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20doesn't%20take%20long%20for%20white%20cushions%20to%20start%20looking%20dingy