ment%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fshopping%2Fartists%2Fbest-post-malone-merch-gifts-1236109201%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fshopping%2Fartists%2Fbest-post-malone-merch-gifts-1236109201%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fshopping%2Fartists%2Fbest-post-malone-merch-gifts-1236109201%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20used%20credit%20card%20rewards%20to%20take%20a%20dream%20vacation%20to%20Belize%20for%20just%20over%20%241%2C000%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20offers%20and%20details%20on%20this%20page%20may%20have%20updated%20or%20changed%20since%20the%20time%20of%20publication.%20See%20our%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravel-rewards-credit-card-went-belize-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20current%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAffiliate%20links%20for%20the%20products%20on%20this%20page%20are%20from%20partners%20that%20compensate%20us%20and%20terms%20apply%20to%20offers%20listed%20(see%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Four-partners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvertiser%20disclosure%20with%20our%20list%20of%20partners%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20details).%20However%2C%20our%20opinions%20are%20our%20own.%20See%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fpersonal-finance-editorial-standards%23rating-credit-cards%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20we%20rate%20credit%20cards%20to%20write%20unbiased%20product%20reviews%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221290%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mariette%20Williams%20smiles%20while%20holding%20a%20coconut%20with%20a%20straw%20sticking%20out.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66be6e791aa2ac29ee31bc64%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22645%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%2C%20Mariette%20Williams.%3Cp%3EMariette%20Williams%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EI%20traveled%20to%20Belize%20with%20friends%20recently%20and%20had%20a%20great%20time%20for%20under%20%241%2C000.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBy%20traveling%20during%20the%20low%20season%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20get%20a%20cheaper%20room%2C%20and%20cheaper%20flights.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EI%20cashed%20in%20points%20from%20my%20travel%20rewards%20credit%20card%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20save%20hundreds.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20summer%2C%20my%20friends%20and%20I%20like%20to%20vacation%20together.%20We%20try%20to%20find%20affordable%20locations%20that%20offer%20beaches%2C%20nice%20accommodations%2C%20and%20good%20food.%20Since%20summer%20is%20the%20low%20season%20in%20most%20of%20Central%20America%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20plan%20a%20trip%20to%20Belize%2C%20which%20is%20known%20for%20its%20affordability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelize%20is%20a%20popular%20vacation%20destination%20because%20of%20its%20warm%20weather%2C%20beaches%2C%20and%20great%20exchange%20rate.%20We%20knew%20a%20large%20part%20of%20our%20budget%20would%20go%20toward%20our%20hotel.%20We%20wanted%20a%20beachfront%20apartment%20at%20an%20adults-only%20property.%20After%20researching%2C%20we%20found%20an%20ideal%20property%20in%20Placencia%2C%20a%20sleepy%20beach%20town%20south%20of%20Belize%20City%2C%20and%20split%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETraveling%20during%20Belize's%20low%20season%20means%20experiencing%20high%20temperatures%20and%20a%20few%20rain%20showers.%20However%2C%20low-season%20travel%20has%20some%20advantages%2C%20such%20as%20uncrowded%20beaches%20and%20restaurants%20and%20deals%20on%20flights%20and%20hotels.%20I%20used%20points%20from%20my%20travel%20rewards%20credit%20card%20and%20spent%20just%20over%20%241%2C000%20in%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20spent%20%24628%20on%20accommodations%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20biggest%20expense%20was%20our%20accommodations.%20We%20stayed%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caribbeanbeachcabanas.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECaribbean%20Beach%20Cabanas%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20offers%20a%20sliding-scale%20discounted%20rate%20for%20booking%20during%20the%20low%20season%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20room%20level.%20We%20booked%20a%20two-bedroom%2C%20two-bathroom%20villa%20with%20a%20fully%20equipped%20kitchen%2C%20living%20room%2C%20and%20an%20oversized%20deck%20that%20overlooked%20the%20hotel%20pool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20total%20cost%20for%20the%20villa%20for%20five%20nights%20was%20%241885%2C%20which%20we%20split%20three%20ways.%20We%20did%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20hotel's%20low%20season%20rates%20(though%20it%20only%20saved%20us%20about%20%2430%20a%20night%20since%20the%20villa%20is%20their%20largest%20unit)%2C%20but%20we%20felt%20like%20we%20got%20our%20money's%20worth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20felt%20comfortable%20splurging%20on%20the%20villa%20because%20the%20hotel%20was%20right%20on%20the%20beach%20and%20within%20walking%20distance%20of%20Placencia's%20main%20street.%20This%20meant%20we%20didn't%20have%20to%20budget%20for%20taxis%20to%20get%20around%20all%20week%2C%20and%20the%20hotel%20also%20offered%20complimentary%20round-trip%20transportation%20from%20the%20local%20airport.%20Although%20there%20were%20less%20expensive%20accommodations%20in%20Placencia%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20stay%20at%20an%20adults-only%20property%2C%20and%20we%20enjoyed%20having%20a%20full%20kitchen%20and%20living%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMy%20flights%20were%20just%20over%20%24100%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20we%20booked%20the%20villa%2C%20I%20set%20a%20tracker%20for%20flights%2C%20and%20I%20found%20a%20good%20deal%20on%20my%20flight.%20I%20booked%20an%20American%20Airlines%20flight%20from%20Miami%20to%20Belize%20City%20and%20spent%20%24272%20on%20a%20roundtrip%20flight%2C%20hundreds%20below%20peak%20prices.%20I'm%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fhow-to-earn-redeem-american-airlines-aadvantage-miles%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Airlines%20AAdvantage%3C%2Fa%3E%20member%2C%20so%20I%20also%20used%20the%20flight%20to%20accumulate%20frequent%20flyer%20miles%2C%20which%20I%20can%20eventually%20cash%20out%20on%20future%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20we%20arrived%20in%20Belize%20City%2C%20we%20had%20two%20options%20for%20getting%20to%20Placencia%3A%20rent%20a%20car%20and%20drive%20for%20two%20to%20three%20hours%20or%20take%20a%20%26quot%3Bpuddle%20jumper%26quot%3B%20plane%20that%20would%20get%20us%20to%20our%20destination%20in%20about%2015%20minutes.%20We%20opted%20for%20the%20plane%20and%20purchased%20the%20additional%20flights%20from%20Belize%20City%20to%20Placencia%20on%20Tropic%20Air%2C%20which%20cost%20%24129%20each%20way%2C%20or%20an%20additional%20%24258%20round%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fbank-of-america-travel-rewards-credit-card-review%5C%22%3EBank%20of%20America%20Travel%20Rewards%3C%2Fa%3E%20credit%20cardholder%2C%20and%20I%20cashed%20in%20%24425%20worth%20of%20travel%20credits%20(which%20were%20applied%20to%20my%20next%20billing%20cycle)%20to%20bring%20the%20cost%20of%20my%20flights%20down%20to%20just%20over%20%24100.%20I%20use%20my%20Bank%20of%20America%20Travel%20Rewards%20card%20for%20nearly%20all%20of%20my%20everyday%20spending.%20The%20card%20doesn't%20have%20an%20annual%20fee%2C%20and%20I%20earn%201.5%20points%20on%20all%20purchases.%20A%20few%20times%20a%20year%2C%20I%20cash%20out%20my%20points%20to%20cover%20flights%20or%20hotels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOur%20food%20and%20activities%20were%20very%20affordable%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFood%20was%20the%20least%20expensive%20part%20of%20our%20trip%20%E2%80%94%20in%20total%2C%20I%20spent%20around%20%24350%20on%20food%20and%20activities.%20Our%20hotel%20offered%20complimentary%20coffee%20and%20pastries%20every%20morning%20for%20breakfast%2C%20and%20we%20ate%20at%20local%20restaurants%20for%20lunch%20and%20dinner.%20Most%20of%20our%20meals%20were%20under%20%2420%2C%20and%20instead%20of%20ordering%20drinks%20at%20each%20meal%2C%20we%20picked%20up%20a%20bottle%20of%20wine%20to%20enjoy%20back%20at%20our%20villa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlencencia%20is%20a%20very%20low-key%20vacation%20spot%2C%20perfect%20for%20lying%20out%20on%20the%20beach%2C%20which%20is%20what%20we%20did%20most%20of%20the%20day.%20We%20alternated%20between%20hanging%20out%20by%20the%20pool%20and%20the%20beach%2C%20and%20the%20hotel%20also%20had%20a%20few%20complimentary%20kayaks%2C%20inner%20tubes%2C%20and%20snorkel%20gear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20explored%20Placencia%20by%20walking%20and%20using%20the%20hotel's%20complimentary%20bikes%20to%20get%20around%20town.%20We%20skipped%20the%20expensive%20excursions%20and%20rented%20a%20golf%20cart%20for%20one%20day%2C%20which%20cost%20%2450%2C%20which%20we%20split%20three%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20came%20in%20just%20over%20my%20%241%2C000%20budget%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20regret%20splurging%20on%20the%20villa%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20because%20I%20was%20able%20to%20accumulate%20points%20for%20my%20flight%20and%20food%20purchases%20I%20charged%20to%20my%20credit%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERewards%20Credit%20Cards%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fbest-rewards-credit-cards%5C%22%3Ebest%20rewards%20credit%20cards%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecan%20be%20a%20great%20way%20to%20earn%20cash%20back%20or%20travel%20rewards%20on%20your%20everyday%20purchases.%20Popular%20cards%20include%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fchase-sapphire-preferred-card-review%5C%22%3EChase%20Sapphire%20Preferred%20card%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2