01.7%20million-square-foot%20office%20skyscraper%20is%20built%20%E2%80%94%20a%20process%20expected%20to%20take%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECitadel%20and%20Citadel%20Securities%2C%20also%20operated%20by%20Griffin%2C%20together%20have%20about%20440%2C000%20square%20feet%20nearby%20at%20425%20Park%20Ave.%2C%20another%20tower%20that%20was%20completed%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20deal%20with%20Citadel%20would%20be%20a%20sign%20of%20activity%20for%20660%20Fifth%20Ave.%20after%20a%20lull.%20Brookfield%20acquired%20the%20building%20from%20Kushner%20Companies%20in%202018%20and%20embarked%20on%20an%20overhaul%2C%20recladding%20the%20wedding-cake-style%20property%20with%20a%20new%20facade%20featuring%20distinct%20rectangular%20windows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Australian%20financial%20institution%20Macquarie%20Group%20signed%20on%20for%20220%2C000%20square%20feet%2C%20the%20hedge%20fund%20Viking%20Global%20took%20nearly%20140%2C000%20square%20feet%2C%20and%20400%20Capital%20Management%2C%20an%20asset%20manager%2C%20grabbed%2026%2C000%20square%20feet%2C%20all%20in%202022.%20Leasing%20quieted%2C%20however%2C%20as%20Brookfield%20raised%20rents%20to%20try%20to%20capitalize%20on%20the%20momentum%2C%20with%20prices%20reaching%20as%20high%20as%20%24200%20per%20square%20foot%20for%20some%20of%20the%20building's%20best%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20executives%20with%20knowledge%20of%20Citadel's%20real-estate%20plans%20said%20the%20firm%20would%20likely%20begin%20moving%20from%20350%20Park%20Ave.%20to%20660%20Fifth%20Ave.%20around%20the%20end%20of%202025.%20It%20could%20take%20five%20or%20more%20years%20to%20demolish%20the%20building%2C%20raise%20the%20new%20tower%2C%20and%20ready%20its%20interior%20for%20occupancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECitadel%20and%20Citadel%20Securities%20plan%20to%20take%20a%20combined%20850%2C000%20square%20feet%20in%20the%20new%20350%20Park%20Ave.%2C%20which%20would%20make%20it%20the%20companies'%20largest%20office%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2