20good%20to%20be%20true.%20It%20is%2C%20a%20scientist%20found.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close%20up%20of%20a%20woman%20injecting%20medication%20into%20the%20skin%20of%20her%20stomach.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bf71375da406397bf68f64%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOnline%20versions%20of%20weight-loss%20drugs%20are%20often%20scams%20or%20pose%20a%20serious%20risk%20of%20contamination%20or%20overdose%2C%20new%20research%20suggests.%3Cp%3Enensuria%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWeight-loss%20drugs%20are%20expensive%2C%20so%20many%20people%20are%20buying%20cheaper%20versions%20online.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20researcher%20at%20UCSD%20bought%20weight-loss%20drugs%20online%20and%20tested%20them.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHis%20results%20underscore%20why%20people%20are%20risking%20dangerous%20side%20effects%20by%20taking%20gray-market%20drugs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20FDA%20approved%20the%20prescription%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-glp-1-drugs-ozempic-wegovy-mounjaro-effects-future-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGLP-1%20weight-loss%20drugs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20been%20hard%20to%20get%20hold%20of%20the%20real%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemand%20is%20so%20high%20for%20semaglutide%2C%20a%20GLP-1%20sold%20under%20the%20brand%20names%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy%2C%20that%20it%20almost%20immediately%20went%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-drug-semaglutide-called-game-changer-for-obesity-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshortage%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20it%20was%20approved%20for%20weight%20control%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20at%20over%20%241%2C000%20for%20a%20month's%20supply%2C%20it's%20a%20tough%20medication%20to%20afford%20even%20if%20you%20can%20access%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENaturally%2C%20that's%20spawned%20a%20wave%20of%20cheaper%20copycat%20drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20have%20watched%20nervously%20as%20the%20resulting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeptides-growth-hormone-hgh-new-health-fad-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egray%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20so-called%20generic%20semaglutide%20has%20ballooned.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPharmacies%20are%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etechnically%20allowed%20to%20make%20their%20own%20versions%20of%20brand-name%20drugs%20under%20specific%20circumstances%20and%20with%20a%20prescription.%20But%20some%20websites%20are%20offering%20the%20drugs%20without%20a%20prescription%2C%20no%20questions%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20begs%20the%20question%3A%20What's%20in%20the%20online%20versions%20of%20semaglutide%2C%20and%20how%20can%20consumers%20know%20what%20they're%20getting%20or%20if%20it's%20safe%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECue%20Timothy%20Mackey%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20San%20Diego%2C%20who%20has%20been%20studying%20the%20online%20market%20for%20counterfeit%20drugs%20for%20decades.%20He%20decided%20to%20buy%20some%20of%20these%20cheaper%2C%20more%20accessible%20weight-loss%20drugs%20himself%20and%20test%20them%20in%20a%20lab%20with%20a%20team%20of%20researchers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20results%2C%20published%20August%202%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjamanetworkopen%2Ffullarticle%2F2821882%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJAMA%20Network%20Open%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20provide%20some%20of%20the%20clearest%20information%20we%20have%20to%20date%20on%20what%20is%20%E2%80%94%20and%20isn't%20%E2%80%94%20in%20knock-off%20versions%20of%20Ozempic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225e5f9e01-a40f-4b4a-8bbd-697032671a84%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20sites%20were%20scamming%20people%20out%20of%20money%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20off-brands%20of%20semaglutide%20are%20illegal%20or%20necessarily%20dangerous.%20Popular%20telehealth%20companies%20typically%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20customers%20to%20obtain%20a%20prescription%20via%20online%20consultation%20and%20provide%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuy-compounded-semaglutide-online-risks-wegovy-ozempic-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompounded%20semaglutide%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20cheaper%20than%20brand-name%20versions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20risks%20involved%20in%20this%20process%2C%20Mackey%20said.%20There's%20less%20supervision%20than%20seeing%20a%20doctor%20in%20person%2C%20plus%20compounded%20medications%20are%20not%20FDA-approved%20and%20can%20have%20unpredictable%20additives.%20However%2C%20the%20pharmacies%20that%20fill%20these%20prescriptions%20are%20regulated%20and%20have%20some%20level%20of%20quality%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMackey's%20team%20was%20specifically%20interested%20in%20what%20he%20called%20the%20highest-risk%20form%20of%20semaglutide%20%E2%80%94%20weight-loss%20drugs%20sold%20online%20without%20a%20prescription.%20They%20gathered%20samples%20of%20these%20products%20to%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20websites%20the%20researchers%20used%20to%20purchase%20and%20test%20the%20products%20appeared%20in%20the%20top%20results%20on%20mainstream%20search%20engines%20and%20have%20millions%20of%20visitors%2C%20according%20to%20an%20analysis%20of%20the%20site%20traffic%2C%20Mackey%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20found%20that%20half%20of%20the%20sites%20were%20advertising%20brand-name%20Ozempic%2C%20which%20cost%20between%20%24190%20and%20%24360%20for%20two%20pens%20plus%20delivery%20fees.%20Ozempic%20was%20in%20shortage%20when%20they%20conducted%20the%20study%2C%20and%20even%20doctors%20were%20struggling%20to%20get%20hold%20of%20the%20real%20drug%20via%20official%20means.%20Predictably%2C%20brand-name%20products%20never%20arrived.%20When%20the%20researchers%20followed%20up%2C%20they%20were%20asked%20to%20pay%20extra%20money%3Cstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20between%20%24650%20and%20%241%2C200%20%E2%80%94%20to%20%26quot%3Bclear%20customs%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20it%20was%20a%20fraud%2C%20the%20researchers%20found%20after%20contacting%20customs%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f605c24d-af31-4755-945f-4ecd13101242%5C%22%3EDangerous%20ingredients%20and%20concentrations%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20sites%20advertised%20generic%20semaglutide.%20They%20did%20deliver%20the%20product%2C%20albeit%20in%20a%20dubious%20form%20with%20inconsistent%20dosages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20one%20thing%2C%20all%20the%20samples%20arrived%20in%20powdered%20form%2C%20requiring%20users%20to%20reconstitute%20it%20using%20special%20sterilized%20water%20before%20injecting%20it.%20(This%20practice%20is%20common%20for%20online%20sales%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeptides-growth-hormone-hgh-new-health-fad-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeptides%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20popular%20category%20of%20fitness%20and%20antiaging%20supplements.)%20Only%20one%20of%20the%20products%20provided%20instructions%20on%20how%20to%20do%20this.%20Doing%20it%20wrong%20poses%20a%20serious%20risk%20of%20contamination%2C%20Mackey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20the%20samples%20were%20advertised%20as%2099%25%20pure%20semaglutide.%20Testing%20revealed%20they%20were%20between%207%25%20and%2014%25%20pure.%20The%20samples%20also%20provided%20higher%20doses%20of%20semaglutide%20than%20the%20label%20suggested%20%E2%80%94%20up%20to%2039%25%20more%20per%20batch%20%E2%80%94%20increasing%20the%20risk%20of%20overdose.%20Too%20much%20semaglutide%20can%20cause%20serious%20gastrointestinal%20side%20effects%20like%20vomiting%2C%20as%20well%20as%20dehydration%2C%20and%20acute%20pancreatitis%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Fdrugs%2Fhuman-drug-compounding%2Ffda-alerts-health-care-providers-compounders-and-patients-dosing-errors-associated-compounded%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFDA%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMackey's%20team%20also%20found%20that%20the%20products%20were%20likely%20research-grade%20semaglutide%20never%20intended%20for%20human%20use.%20The%20websites%20used%20creative%20marketing%20language%20and%20imagery%20to%20imply%20their%20products%20were%20intended%20for%20people%2C%20without%20saying%20it%20directly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20products%20also%20contained%20high%20levels%20of%20endotoxin%2C%20a%20harmful%20substance%20found%20in%20bacterial%20cells%20(although%20no%20live%20bacteria%20were%20seen).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPoison-control%20centers%20saw%20a%20massive%20spike%20in%20semaglutide%20overdoses%20last%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2023%2F12%2F13%2Fhealth%2Fsemaglutide-overdoses-wellness%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20Based%20on%20his%20team's%20results%2C%20Mackey%20is%20not%20surprised.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20clear%20sign%20of%20a%20product%20not%20intended%20for%20human%20use%2C%26quot%3B%20Mackey%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20bottom%20line%20there%20is%20that%20there%20are%20discrepancies%20in%20their%20manufacturing%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229e4b0736-b0e4-4421-9ddc-3daac72381db%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECounterfeit%20Ozempic%20isn't%20going%20away%2C%20so%20buyer%20beware%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMackey%20said%20a%20wave%20of%20telehealth%20services%20and%20online%20providers%20have%20made%20it%20easier%20than%20ever%20to%20get%20prescriptions%20and%20medications%20online.%20But%20it's%20also%20harder%20to%20spot%20a%20scam%20now%20than%20when%20everything%20came%20from%20brick-and-mortar%20pharmacy%20after%20a%20face-to-face%20with%20a%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20average%20user%20is%20more%20confused%20about%20how%20to%20get%20this%20legitimately%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIllicit%20websites%20can%20be%20convincing%2C%20but%20if%20they%20emphasize%20their%20weight-loss%20medications%20don't%20require%20a%20prescription%2C%20that's%20a%20major%20red%20flag%2C%20according%20to%20Mackey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20warning%20sign%20is%20cost.%20Brand-name%20semaglutide%20can%20set%20you%20back%20more%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-weight-loss-meds-injections-compare-costs-results-side-effects%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%241%2C000%20a%20month%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20a%20product%20is%20listed%20online%20for%20significantly%20cheaper%2C%20you're%20likely%20to%20get%20what%20you%20paid%20for%20%E2%80%94%20an%20inferior%20or%20counterfeit%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20providers%20are%20advertising%20at%20%24200%2C%20that's%20because%20they're%20not%20real%2C%20but%20still%20they're%20advertising%20at%20a%20lower%20price%20point%20and%20that's%20going%20to%20be%20attractive%20to%20consumers%2C%26quot%3B%20Mackey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20risks%20and%20the%20FDA's%20efforts%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20scammers%20and%20shady%20products%2C%20the%20market%20for%20weight-loss%20drugs%20is%20just%20too%20big%2C%20too%20new%2C%20and%20too%20messy%20to%20expect%20counterfeiters%20will%20stop%20anytime%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20be%20something%20endemic%20in%20our%20supply%20chain%20because%20of%20how%20popular%20the%20market%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Mackey%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20kind%20of%20an%20arms%20race%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscientist-cheaper-ozempic-sold-online-contains-dangerous-ingredients-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723832197000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bf715d1aa2ac29ee31deaa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscientist-cheape