Governor%20On%20Kolkata%20Rape%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20caustic%20comments%20directed%20at%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%20after%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20trainee%20doctor%20at%20a%20Kolkata%20hospital%20and%20the%20subsequent%20vandalism%20in%20the%20campus%2C%20Governor%20CV%20Ananda%20Bose%20has%20said%20%26quot%3Bvandals%20and%20scandals%26quot%3B%20are%20marring%20civic%20life%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMincing%20no%20words%20in%20a%20wide-ranging%20interview%20with%20NDTV%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20West%20Bengal%20governor%20held%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20responsible%20for%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20state%2C%20claimed%20women%20medical%20students%20have%20told%20him%20that%20their%20families%20want%20them%20to%20leave%20the%20profession%2C%20and%20said%20it%20was%20disheartening%20that%20such%20incidents%20were%20taking%20place%20in%20a%20land%20where%20one%20of%20its%20most%20illustrious%20sons%20had%20spoken%20of%20the%20mind%20being%20without%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bose%20also%20said%20that%20he%20has%20opened%20a%20home%20in%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%2C%20named%20after%20the%2031-year-old%20trainee%20doctor%20who%20was%20raped%20and%20killed%20at%20the%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20last%20week.%20The%20woman%20has%20been%20given%20the%20name%20'Abhaya'%20(fearless)%20and%20the%20governor%20said%20students%20who%20feel%20threatened%20will%20be%20valued%20guests%20at%20the%20'Abhaya%20Home'.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20the%20politics%20that%20has%20come%20to%20surround%20the%20handling%20of%20the%20investigation%20and%20the%20protests%20by%20doctors%20and%20medical%20students%2C%20the%20governor%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BScandals%20and%20vandals%20are%20marring%20the%20civic%20life%20of%20Bengal.%20I%20was%20interacting%20with%20some%20medical%20students.%20They%20told%20me%2C%20'Please%20deliver%20us%20from%20the%20fear%20psychosis.%20Please%20give%20us%20protection.%20We%20have%20no%20security%20inside%20the%20campus%20and%20now%20there%20is%20no%20security%20outside.'%20That%20is%20the%20wailing%20of%20the%20youth%2C%20particularly%20those%20in%20the%20medical%20profession.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20girl%20students%20told%20me%20they%20have%20nowhere%20to%20go%2C%20they%20have%20no%20security.%20'Our%20parents%20are%20asking%20us%20to%20leave%20the%20profession%2C%20give%20back%20the%20bond%20money.%20Come%20back.%20Life%20is%20more%20important%20than%20this%2C'%20they%20told%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20a%20girl%20was%20afraid%20the%20%26quot%3Bgoons%26quot%3B%20would%20follow%20her%20to%20her%20rural%20posting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'What%20Bengal%20Thinks%20Today...'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20youth%20are%20neither%20creations%20of%20the%20past%20nor%20custodians%20of%20the%20present%2C%20Mr%20Bose%20said%20they%20are%20the%20creators%20of%20the%20future%20and%20it%20was%20distressing%20to%20see%20them%20having%20to%20plead%20for%20their%20security%20like%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20happens%20on%20the%20street%20in%20the%20name%20of%20politics%20is%20none%20of%20my%20business.%20But%20the%20fact%20remains%20that%20there%20is%20a%20growing%20fear%20in%20Bengal's%20society.%20There%20is%20violence%20everywhere.%20And%20all%20this%20is%20happening%20in%20Bengal%2C%20about%20which%20Gopalkrishna%20Gokhale%20once%20said%2C%20'What%20Bengal%20thinks%20today%2C%20India%20thinks%20tomorrow'.%20Is%20this%20the%20same%20Bengal%20about%20which%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%20said%2C%20'Where%20the%20mind%20is%20without%20fear%20and%20the%20head%20is%20held%20high'%3F%20Democracy%20is%20plummeting%20into%20mobocracy.%20That%20is%20the%20distressing%20spectacle%20that%20we%20see%20around%20us.%20That's%20what%20worries%20me%20as%20a%20governor%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbhaya%20Home%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20governor%20said%20he%20has%20faith%20in%20the%20CBI%2C%20which%20is%20investigating%20the%20case%2C%20and%20detailed%20a%20three-pronged%20approach%20that%20he%20has%20taken%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20students'%20grievances%20are%20addressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20has%20utilised%20his%20powers%20under%20Article%20167%20of%20the%20Constitution%20and%20given%20instructions%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20apart%20from%20taking%20up%20the%20matter%20with%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20measure%2C%20an%20interim%20one%2C%20is%20the%20opening%20of%20the%20'Abhaya%20Home'%20at%20Raj%20Bhavan%2C%20the%20governor's%20official%20residence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20student%20who%20feels%20threatened%20can%20come%20here.%20They%20will%20be%20honoured%20guests%2C%20valued%20guests%20of%20the%20governor.%20Whatever%20other%20long-term%20measures%20are%20to%20be%20taken%2C%20I%20have%20already%20taken%20up%20with%20the%20state%20government%20as%20well%20as%20with%20the%20central%20government%2C%20including%20adequate%20legislation%20guaranteeing%20security%20for%20medicos%20and%20paramedics...%20Everything%20that%20is%20possible%20for%20confidence%20building%20will%20be%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bose%20emphasised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPresident's%20Rule%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmploying%20wordplay%20and%20keeping%20his%20cards%20close%20to%20his%20chest%20while%20answering%20a%20question%20on%20the%20opposition's%20demand%20for%20President's%20Rule%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20the%20governor%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDemand%20is%20demand%2C%20let's%20see%20what%20the%20supply%20is.%20As%20governor%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20be%20circumspect%20on%20such%20issues.%20The%20Constitution%20has%20many%20options.%20I%20reserve%20my%20options%20at%20this%20moment...%20I%20do%20not%20want%20to%20come%20out%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20about%20what%20I'm%20going%20to%20do%20next%20under%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Chief%20Minister%20Responsible%201st%2C%202nd%20and%203rd'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHolding%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20responsible%20for%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20the%20Governor%20said%20that%20while%20the%20cabinet%20has%20collective%20responsibility%2C%20the%20buck%20stops%20with%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cabinet%20has%20collective%20responsibility.%20Whatever%20happens%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20first%20responsibility%20is%20that%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20the%20second%20responsibility%20is%20that%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20the%20third%20responsibility%20is%20that%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bose%20insisted%20he%20has%20been%20getting%20frantic%20calls%20from%20medical%20professionals%20all%20over%20India%2C%20who%20have%20told%20him%20they%20are%20afraid.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20medical%20fraternity%20stood%20as%20a%20one-man%20army%20against%20Covid%20and%20saved%20this%20country.%20We%20owe%20it%20to%20them.%20They%20don't%20deserve%20such%20treatment.%20It%20is%20said%20medicines%20can%20cure%20diseases%20but%20only%20a%20doctor%20can%20cure%20patients.%20That%20is%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20medical%20fraternity%2C%20including%20the%20paramedics.%20We%20cannot%20let%20them%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stressed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723831680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fnmisjdio_cv-ananda-bose-interview_625x300_16_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-rape-cv-ananda-bose-rg-kar-hospital-vandals-scandals-marring-civic-life-in-bengal-governor-on-kolkata-rape-6353545%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20caustic%20comments%20directed%20at%20the%20Bengal%20government%20after%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20