0it's%20always%20surprising.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FrsuqSn7ifpU%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22First%20Look%20Inside%20Blue%20Origin's%20New%20Glenn%20Factory%20w%2F%20Jeff%20Bezos!%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20factory%20tour%20was%20also%20an%20opportunity%20for%20Bezos%20to%20show%20off%20his%20nerdy%20side.%20The%20Amazon%20cofounder%20talked%20excitedly%20about%20the%20intricacies%20of%20the%20technology%20powering%20New%20Glenn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rocket%2C%20which%20is%20set%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblue-origin-new-shepard-delay-explainer-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efly%20for%20the%20first%20time%20later%20this%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20a%20partially%20reusable%20heavy-lift%20launch%20vehicle%20designed%20to%20lift%2045%20metric%20tons%20to%20low-Earth%20orbit.%20By%20comparison%2C%20SpaceX's%20Falcon%20Heavy%2C%20which%20powers%20Starship%2C%20can%20lift%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.spacex.com%2Fvehicles%2Ffalcon-heavy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enearly%2064%20metric%20tons%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20orbit%20and%20is%20also%20partially%20reusable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBezos%20showed%20off%20New%20Glenn's%20Stage%20One%2C%20which%20is%20powered%20by%20seven%20BE-4%20engines%20%E2%80%94%20powerful%20liquid%20oxygen%20and%20liquefied%20natural%20gas-fueled%20combustion%20engines.%20He%20also%20explained%20the%20welding%20process%20of%20the%20tanks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20very%20high-performance%20way%20to%20build%20the%20tank%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20especially%20because%20it's%20a%20reusable%20vehicle%2C%20you%20get%20to%20reuse%20all%20that%20high-performance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20Glenn%20is%20a%20two-stage%20rocket%20%E2%80%94%20following%20its%20launch%2C%20Stage%20One%20will%20separate%20from%20the%20Second%20Stage%20and%20autonomously%20descend%20back%20into%20a%20landing%20platform%20to%20be%20reused.%20Two%20BE-3U%20engines%20will%20then%20propel%20the%20Second%20Stage%20into%20space%20to%20deliver%20its%20payload.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBezos%20said%20the%20vehicle%20is%20designed%20to%20be%20turned%20around%20in%2016%20days%20and%20last%20for%20a%20minimum%20of%2025%20missions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20hoping%20it%20will%20eventually%20be%20much%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Bezos%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe'd%20like%20to%20get%20to%20at%20least%20a%20hundred.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBezos%20also%20talked%20about%20his%20past%20salvage%20mission%20in%20the%20Atlantic%20to%20recover%20Project%20Apollo's%20Saturn%20V%20engines%2C%20which%20powered%20the%20Apollo%2011%20to%20the%20moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20sitting%20in%20my%20living%20room%20one%20day%20and%20I%20said%2C%20'You%20know%2C%20I%20wonder%20if%20you%20could%20find%20those%20F1%20engines%20from%20Apollo%2011%20sitting%20on%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20Atlantic%20somewhere%2C'%26quot%3B%20Bezos%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20went%20to%20Google%20and%20I%20typed%20in%20Apollo%2011%20booster%20impact%20coordinates.%20And%20they%20popped%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20I%20thought%2C%20this%20is%20gonna%20be%20the%20easiest%20thing%20I've%20ever%20done%2C%20I'm%20gonna%20go%20recover%20those%20engines.%20Of%20course%2C%20that%20was%20the%20only%20part%20of%20it%20that%20was%20easy.%20It%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20incredibly%20hard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20reusability%20leads%20to%20affordability%2C%20which%20is%20Bezo's%20main%20goal.%20He%20said%20that%20although%20manufacturing%20techniques%20have%20been%20massively%20improved%2C%20most%20major%20aspects%20of%20rocketry%20were%20invented%20in%20the%201960s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20haven't%20really%20changed%2C%20so%20our%20job%20today%20is%20not%20to%20do%20better%20than%20they%20did%20at%20spaceflight.%20It's%20to%20make%20it%20more%20affordable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBezos%20explained%20the%20company%20developed%20a%20reusable%20thermal%20protection%20system%20that%20doesn't%20need%20to%20be%20touched%20up%2C%20another%20aspect%20of%20the%20rocket's%20operable%20reusability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EViewers%20were%20also%20able%20to%20see%20the%20rocket's%20hydrogen-powered%20Upper%20Stage%20and%20its%20Aft%20Section%2C%20where%20the%20seven%20BE-4%20engines%20are%20mounted%20in%20the%20base.%20Bezos%20additionally%20took%20Dodd%20to%20its%20forward%20section%2C%20which%20has%20four%20fins%20that%20are%20the%20%26quot%3Blargest%20hydraulic%20actuators%20on%20a%20space%20aero%20surface%26quot%3B%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20good%20aerospace%20hardware%20does%20look%20like%20art%20because%20you're%20just%20going%20for%20function%2C%26quot%3B%20Bezos%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20there's%20something%20when%20you%20go%20for%20that%20last%201%25%20of%20function%2C%20it%20really%20makes%20things%20beautiful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBezos%20wasn't%20the%20first%20billionaire%20that%20YouTuber%20Tim%20Dodd%20landed%20a%20factory%20tour%20with%20%E2%80%94%20he's%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-spacex-starfactory-tour-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterviewed%20Elon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20multiple%20times%2C%20recently%20touring%20SpaceX's%20new%20%26quot%3BStarfactory%26quot%3B%20where%20its%20Starship%20rocket%20is%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-shows-blue-origin-new-glenn-rocket-factory-tour-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22