y%20dismissed%20in%202022%20and%20ordered%20X%20to%20pay%20him%20a%20huge%20amount%20-%20the%20largest%20sum%20the%20agency%20has%20ever%20awarded%2C%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2Feurope%2F2024%2F08%2F14%2Fx-ordered-to-pay-550000-to-irish-employee-fired-for-not-replying-to-elon-musk-yes-or-resign-extremely-hardcore-ultimatum%2F%5C%22%3Eoutlet%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202022%2C%20shortly%20after%20Mr%20Musk's%20takeover%20of%20X%2C%20the%20billionaire%20sent%20a%20company-wide%20email%20demanding%20employees%20commit%20to%20working%20%26quot%3Blong%20hours%20at%20high%20intensity%26quot%3B%20or%20receive%20a%20big%20payout.%20Employees%2C%20including%20Mr%20Rooney%2C%20were%20given%20a%20day%20to%20click%20%26quot%3Byes%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20email%20to%20accept%20the%20new%20working%20conditions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commission%20heard%20that%20X%20maintained%20that%20the%20employee%20had%20resigned%20voluntarily%20after%20he%20failed%20to%20tick%20a%20box%20committing%20to%20new%20unspecified%20working%20arrangements%20in%20an%20email%20from%20the%20company's%20new%20owner%20Elon%20Musk.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbill-gates-escaped-tightly-scheduled-life-by-visiting-warren-buffett-reveals-new-book-6351408%5C%22%3EBill%20Gates%20Escaped%20Tightly%20Scheduled%20Life%20By%20Visiting%20Warren%20Buffett%2C%20Reveals%20New%20Book%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Irish%20Workplace%20Relations%20Commission%20refused%20to%20buy%20this%20argument%20and%20ruled%20that%20not%20clicking%20%26quot%3Byes%26quot%3B%20in%20response%20to%20the%20email%20did%20not%20constitute%20an%20act%20of%20resignation.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20OK%20for%20Mr.%20Musk%2C%20or%20indeed%20any%20large%20company%20to%20treat%20employees%20in%20such%20a%20manner%20in%20this%20country%20or%20jurisdiction.%20The%20record%20award%20reflects%20the%20seriousness%20and%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complainant's%20solicitor%20Barry%20Kenny%20said%2C%20per%20the%20outlet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20this%20is%20one%20of%20the%20cases%20that%20sprung%20up%20since%20Mr%20Musk%20purchased%20the%20micro-blogging%20site.%20Multiple%20lawsuits%20have%20already%20alleged%20that%20X%20employees%20did%20not%20receive%20their%20promised%20severance%20benefits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%20acquired%20Twitter%20in%20October%202022%20in%20a%20%2444%20billion%20deal.%20He%20laid%20off%20almost%20half%20the%20employees%20shortly%20after%20his%20takeover%20of%20the%20company%20and%20sent%20a%20hardcore%20ultimatum%20to%20the%20remaining%20staff.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723829940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F9r47i6pc_elon-musk-ians_625x300_14_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musks-x-ordered-to-pay-rs-5-crore-to-employee-fired-for-not-responding-to-billionaires-email-6353219%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk's%20microblogging%20site%20X%20has%20been%20ordered%20to%20pay%20compensation%20to%20a%20former%20employee%20in%20an%20unfair%20dismissal%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musks-x-ordered-to-pay-rs-5-crore-to-employee-fired-for-not-responding-to-billionaires-email-6353219%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Foreign%20exchange%20rules%20amended%3A%20Cross-border%20share%20swaps%20eased%20by%20govt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723829851000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-05%2F21%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1716311180-8322.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2