y8xqy0jv24o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Parents%20Gave%20Names%20Of%20Interns%2C%20Doctors%20To%20CBI%20In%20Kolkata%20Horror%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20parents%20of%20the%20trainee%20doctor%20who%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered%20at%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20told%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20that%20several%20interns%20and%20physicians%20from%20the%20hospital%20may%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20crime%2C%20an%20officer%20said%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parents%20also%20gave%20the%20CBI%20the%20names%20of%20people%20who%20they%20suspect%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20their%20daughter's%20rape%20and%20murder%20at%20the%20state-run%20hospital.%20The%20CBI%20is%20investigating%20the%20case%20under%20an%20order%20from%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20parents%20told%20us%20that%20they%20suspect%20the%20involvement%20of%20multiple%20people%20behind%20the%20sexual%20assault%20and%20murder%20of%20their%20daughter.%20They%20have%20given%20names%20of%20a%20few%20interns%20and%20doctors%20who%20worked%20with%20her%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20CBI%20officer%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20is%20prioritising%20the%20questioning%20of%20these%20individuals%2C%20as%20well%20as%20officers%20from%20the%20Kolkata%20Police%20who%20were%20part%20of%20the%20initial%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20identified%20at%20least%2030%20suspects%20and%20have%20started%20questioning%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CBI%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fn3vt11qg_kolkata-rape-murder_625x300_16_August_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20today%20summoned%20a%20house%20staff%20member%20and%20two%20post-graduate%20trainees%20who%20were%20on%20duty%20with%20the%20doctor%20the%20night%20she%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered.%20The%20CBI%20took%20the%20former%20hospital%20principal%2C%20Dr%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20for%20questioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Ghosh%20had%20resigned%20two%20days%20after%20the%20woman's%20body%20was%20found.%20He%20said%20he%20feared%20being%20attacked%20and%20sought%20protection%20from%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%2C%20which%20directed%20him%20to%20approach%20a%20single%20Bench.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20made%20the%20arrested%20accused%20-%20a%20civic%20volunteer%20-%20walk%20through%20a%20reconstruction%20of%20the%20crime%20scene%20using%20an%20advanced%203D%20method%20in%20the%20seminar%20hall%20of%20the%20hospital%2C%20the%20officer%20said.%20The%20body%20of%20the%20post-graduate%20trainee%20was%20found%20in%20the%20seminar%20room%20on%20August%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWest%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20today%20accused%20the%20opposition%20CPI(M)%20and%20the%20BJP%20of%20orchestrating%20vandalism%20at%20RG%20Kar%20Hospital%20and%20trying%20to%20distort%20the%20truth%20behind%20the%20rape-murder%20of%20the%20woman%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20the%20truth%20to%20come%20out%2C%20but%20some%20quarters%20are%20spreading%20lies%20to%20mislead%20people.%20Attempts%20are%20being%20made%20to%20hide%20the%20truth%20by%20circulating%20fake%20news%20on%20social%20media.%20We%20condemn%20these%20activities.%20We%20want%20the%20culprits%20to%20be%20punished%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20while%20addressing%20a%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20strong%20retort%20to%20her%2C%20BJP%20spokesperson%20Gaurav%20Bhatia%20called%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%20leaders%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20vultures%26quot%3B%20who%20speak%20out%20on%20crimes%20against%20women%20as%20per%20their%20political%20convenience.%20Mr%20Bhatia%20termed%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20other%20leaders%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20vultures%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20said%20they%20should%20rise%20above%20their%20vote%20bank%20politics%20and%20%26quot%3Bbreak%20their%20silence%26quot%3B%20on%20such%20heinous%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20silence%20will%20cost%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20dearly.%20These%20people%20are%20not%20politicians%20or%20public%20leaders%2C%20they%20are%20political%20vultures%20who%20speak%20out%20on%20crimes%20against%20sisters%20and%20daughters%20after%20seeing%20which%20state%20government%20is%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20law%20and%20order%20has%20collapsed%20in%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20the%20case%20has%20come%20to%20the%20CBI.%20Soon%20all%20the%20guilty%20will%20be%20given%20the%20harshest%20punishment%2C%20no%20accused%20will%20be%20spared%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20big%20a%20leader%20is%20protecting%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtests%20are%20being%20held%20across%20the%20country%20by%20medical%20students%20and%20doctors%2C%20demanding%20a%20law%20to%20ensure%20safety%20in%20hospitals%20and%20workplaces%20of%20medical%20professionals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20PTI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723829160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fhbpaiklg_kolkata-protest_625x300_16_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkolkata-news%2Fparents-gave-names-of-interns-doctors-to-cbi-in-kolkata-horror-sources-6353432%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20parents%20of%20the%20trainee%20doctor%20who%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered%20at%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20told%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20that%20several%20interns%20an