%20Deposits%20With%20SBI%20And%20PNB%2C%20Karnataka%20Hits%20Pause%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Karnataka%20government%20has%20paused%20its%20order%20suspending%20all%20transactions%20with%20the%20Central%20government-run%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%20and%20Punjab%20National%20Bank%20(PNB)%20just%20three%20days%20after%20it%20was%20issued%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20banks%20have%20sought%20some%20time%20to%20resolve%20the%20issues.%20The%20order%20has%20been%20paused%20for%2015%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20had%20directed%20all%20state%20departments%20to%20close%20their%20accounts%20with%20these%20banks%20and%20recover%20their%20deposits%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccounts%20held%20in%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20and%20Punjab%20National%20Bank%20by%20state%20government%20departments%2C%20public%20enterprises%2C%20corporations%2C%20local%20bodies%2C%20universities%2C%20and%20other%20institutions%20must%20be%20terminated%20forthwith.%20Additionally%2C%20no%20further%20deposits%20or%20investments%20are%20to%20be%20made%20in%20these%20banks%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state's%20finance%20department%20had%20referred%20to%20an%20alleged%20fraud%20involving%20funds%20of%20the%20Karnataka%20Industrial%20Area%20Development%20Board.%20It%20has%20been%20alleged%20that%20money%20had%20been%20siphoned%20off%20with%20the%20involvement%20of%20bank%20officials%20from%20accounts%20in%20the%20Punjab%20National%20Bank.%20The%20government%20said%20the%20case%20has%20been%20pending%20in%20courts%20and%20several%20crores%20have%20still%20not%20been%20refunded.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20State%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20had%20deposited%20money%20with%20SBI%20bank%2C%20which%20was%20allegedly%20adjusted%20along%20with%20a%20loan%20for%20a%20private%20company%20using%20forged%20documents%20in%202013.%20This%20case%20is%20also%20pending%20in%20court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIssuing%20a%20statement%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20government%20said%20its%20earlier%20directive%20had%20been%20paused%20because%20of%20requests%20made%20by%20both%20banks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20(Wednesday's)%20action%20was%20taken%20in%20response%20to%20the%20alleged%20fraud%20in%20the%20bank%20branches%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20non-repayment%20of%20fixed%20deposits%20made%20by%20the%20Karnataka%20State%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20(KSPCB)%20and%20the%20Karnataka%20Industrial%20Area%20Development%20Board%20(KIADB).%20Despite%20prolonged%20correspondence%20and%20meetings%2C%20these%20issues%20remained%20unresolved%20since%202012-13%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20August%2016%2C%202024%2C%20both%20banks%20submitted%20written%20representations%20to%20the%20government%2C%20requesting%20a%2015-day%20period%20to%20resolve%20the%20matter.%20The%20same%20day%2C%20senior%20bank%20officials%20met%20with%20higher%20officials%20of%20the%20Finance%20Department%20and%20reiterated%20their%20request.%20After%20considering%20the%20banks'%20requests%2C%20the%20Honourable%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20directed%20officials%20of%20the%20Finance%20Department%20to%20keep%20the%20circular%20in%20abeyance%20for%2015%20days.%20This%20will%20allow%20the%20banks%20sufficient%20time%20to%20address%20the%20issues%20and%20redress%20the%20concerns%20of%20the%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMoney%20Transfer%20'Scam'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20comes%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20a%20political%20slugfest%20between%20the%20Congress-ruled%20Karnataka%20government%20and%20the%20opposition%20BJP%20over%20the%20alleged%20money%20transfer%20scam%20involving%20the%20state-run%20Karnataka%20Maharshi%20Valmiki%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20Development%20Corporation%20Ltd.%20The%20alleged%20scam%20had%20been%20revealed%20after%20the%20corporation's%20accounts%20superintendent%2C%20Chandrashekhar%20P%2C%20died%20by%20suicide%20on%20May%2026%20and%20left%20a%20note%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20note%20claimed%20that%20Rs%20187%20crore%20belonging%20to%20the%20corporation%20was%20transferred%20without%20authorisation%20and%20Rs%2088.62%20crore%20out%20of%20the%20total%20amount%20was%20then%20moved%20to%20other%20accounts%2C%20including%20those%20belonging%20to%20IT%20companies%20as%20well%20as%20a%20cooperative%20bank%20based%20in%20Hyderabad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723822200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Frcb273g4_state-bank-of-india-sbi-building-ani_625x300_11_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-days-after-big-order-on-deposits-with-sbi-and-pnb-karnataka-hits-pause-6352679%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Karnataka%20government%20has%20paused%20its%20order%20suspending%20all%20transactions%20with%20the%20Central%20government-run%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%20and%20Punjab%20National%20Bank%20(PNB)%20just%20three%20days%20after%20it%20was%20issued.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-days-after-big-order-on-deposits-with-sbi-and-pnb-karnataka-hits-pause-6352679%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BTime%20Was%20Not%20Fair...%26quot%3B%3A%20Vinesh%20Breaks%20Silence%20On%20Olympics%20Disqualification%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVinesh%20Phogat%20has%20finally%20broken%20her%20silence%20on%20her%20heart-breaking%20disqualification%20from%20the%20women's%2050kg%20final%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%202024.%20The%20star%20wrestler%20had%20made%20history%20by%20becoming%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20to%20enter%20a%20wrestling%20event%20final%20at%20the%20Olympics.%20But%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20her%20event%20on%20August%207%2C%20Vinesh%20was%20fo