I%20want%20to%20say%20is%20that%20we%20did%20not%20give%20up%2C%20our%20efforts%20did%20not%20stop%2C%20and%20we%20did%20not%20surrender%20but%20the%20clock%20stopped%20and%20the%20time%20was%20not%20fair%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22zxx%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F8iu2vs21Wq%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F8iu2vs21Wq%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20(%40Phogat_Vinesh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPhogat_Vinesh%2Fstatus%2F1824454938946310658%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2016%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20was%20my%20fate.%20To%20my%20team%2C%20my%20fellow%20Indians%20and%20my%20family%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20the%20goal%20that%20we%20were%20working%20towards%20and%20what%20we%20had%20planned%20to%20achieve%20is%20unfinished%2C%20that%20something%20might%20always%20remain%20missing%2C%20and%20that%20things%20might%20never%20be%20the%20same%20again.%20Maybe%20under%20different%20circumstances%2C%20I%20could%20see%20myself%20playing%20till%202032%2C%20because%20the%20fight%20in%20me%20and%20wrestling%20in%20me%20will%20always%20be%20there.%20I%20can't%20predict%20what%20the%20future%20holds%20for%20me%2C%20and%20what%20awaits%20me%20in%20this%20journey%20next%2C%20but%20I%20am%20sure%20that%20I%20will%20continue%20to%20fight%20always%20for%20what%20I%20believe%20in%20and%20for%20the%20right%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723821960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fauvrj4sg_vinesh-phogat_625x300_15_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics%2Ftime-was-not-fair-vinesh-phogat-breaks-silence-on-what-she-went-through-during-olympics-disqualification-6352568%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20August%207%20till%20August%2015%2C%20Vinesh%20never%20opened%20on%20what%20she%20went%2