-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbpcl-sets-up-first-of-its-kind-biofuel-blend-bunker-at-mumbai-port-124081601554_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shocks%2C%203rd-Degree%20Torture%3A%20Cops%2C%20Doctor%20To%20Be%20Charged%20For%20Custodial%20Death%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOver%20nine%20years%20after%20a%2022-year-old%20accused%20of%20chain%20snatching%20died%20in%20police%20custody%20after%20allegedly%20being%20subjected%20to%20third-degree%20torture%20and%20electric%20shocks%2C%20a%20Bhopal%20District%20Court%20has%20ordered%20the%20filing%20of%20charges%20against%20eight%20people%2C%20including%20a%20former%20jailer%2C%20police%20officials%20and%20a%20doctor.%20The%20charges%20will%20include%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20murder%2C%20destruction%20of%20evidence%20and%20other%20serious%20offences.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohsin%2C%2022%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20by%20the%20Crime%20Branch%20on%20June%204%2C%202015%2C%20on%20allegations%20of%20chain%20snatching%20and%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20TT%20Nagar%20Police%20Station%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20where%20a%20nightmare%20began.%20According%20to%20the%20court's%20findings%2C%20Mohsin%20was%20subjected%20to%20third-degree%20torture%2C%20given%20electric%20shocks%20after%20being%20made%20to%20wear%20a%20helmet%2C%20thrashed%20and%20restrained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20police%20officials%20allegedly%20demanded%20a%20bribe%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20from%20Mohsin's%20family%20and%20the%20situation%20escalated%20when%20his%20family%20couldn't%20meet%20their%20demands.%20The%20court%20was%20told%20Mohsin%20was%20falsely%20charged%20and%20then%20imprisoned%20in%20Bhopal%20Central%20Jail.%20The%2022-year-old%20was%20thrashed%20again%20there%2C%C2%A0%20leading%20to%20his%20eventual%20death%20on%20June%2023%2C%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohsin%20was%20also%20labelled%20mentally%20deranged%20which%2C%20experts%20said%2C%20raises%20a%20big%20question%20-%20a%20person%20accused%20of%20chain%20snatching%20is%20unlikely%20to%20suddenly%20become%20mentally%20challenged%20upon%20reaching%20jail%2C%20so%20how%20did%20that%20happen%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Mohsin%20was%20truly%20mad%2C%20how%20could%20he%20be%20tried%20as%20a%20criminal%3F%20And%20if%20he%20was%20a%20criminal%2C%20how%20could%20he%20suddenly%20become%20mad%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20legal%20expert%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedical%20professionals%20allegedly%20fabricated%20a%20report%20declaring%20Mohsin%20mentally%20challenged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20most%20shocking%20aspect%20of%20the%20entire%20chain%20of%20events%20was%20yet%20to%20come.%20After%20his%20death%20in%20Bhopal%20Central%20Jail%2C%20Mohsin's%20lifeless%20body%20was%20referred%20to%20Gwalior%20by%20train%20for%20%26quot%3Bmental%20treatment.%26quot%3B%20Upon%20arrival%20in%20Gwalior%2C%20the%20body%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20ICU%20of%20the%20Jaya%20Arogya%20Hospital%2C%20where%20he%20was%20finally%20declared%20dead%20on%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Not%20Final%20Justice'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohsin's%20mother%2C%20Seema%20Rais%2C%20says%20the%20death%20of%20her%20son%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bfalse%26quot%3B%20accusations%20against%20him%20and%20the%20alleged%20involvement%20of%20cops%2C%20jailers%20and%20doctors%20haunt%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fpf2etfco_mohsin-mother_625x300_16_August_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20court%20has%20made%20the%20right%20decision%2C%20but%20this%20is%20not%20the%20final%20justice.%20My%20son%20was%20kept%20in%20handcuffs%20under%20a%20table%2C%20moved%20from%20one%20police%20station%20to%20another%20and%20ultimately%20died%20in%20jail.%20The%20police%20demanded%20money%20we%20couldn't%20afford.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20ordered%20the%20filing%20of%20charges%20against%20a%20police%20station%20in-charge%2C%20a%20sub-inspector%2C%20two%20assistant%20sub-inspectors%2C%20a%20jailer%2C%20and%20a%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYawar%20Khan%2C%20who%20is%20representing%20Mohsin's%20family%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20court's%20detailed%20order%20exposes%20the%20brutality%20Mohsin%20faced.%20Even%20higher%20courts%20have%20recognised%20the%20need%20for%20strict%20punishment%20in%20this%20case%2C%20including%20charges%20of%20conspiracy%20and%20murder.%20The%20accused%20now%20face%20the%20threat%20of%20being%20imprisoned%20for%20life%20or%20even%20the%20death%20penalty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohsin's%20tragic%20story%20is%20just%20one%20among%20many.%20According%20to%20government%20statistics%20presented%20in%20Parliament%20in%202023%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20has%20seen%2050%20deaths%20in%20police%20custody%20in%20five%20years%20and%20687%20such%20deaths%20were%20recorded%20nationally%20during%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20special%20director%20general%20of%20police%20Shailendra%20Srivastava%20said%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20deeply%20troubling%20when%20someone%20dies%20in%20police%20custody.%20The%20use%20of%20third-degree%20torture%20is%20a%20gross%20violation%20of%20human%20rights%20and%20has%20no%20place%20in%20a%20civilised%20society.%20The%20consequences%20are%20severe%2C%20not%20just%20for%20the%20victims%20but%20for%20the%20police%20force%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723818720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Falsb6t6o_mohsin-custodial-death_625x300_16_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshocks-3rd-degree-torture-cops-doctor-to-be-charged-for-custodial-death-6352178%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Over%20nine%20years%20after%20a%2022-year-old%20accused%20of%20chain%20snatching%20died%20in%20police%20custody%20after%20allegedly%20being%20subjected%20to%20third-degree%20torture%20and%20electric%20shocks%2C%20a%20Bhopal%20District%20Court%20has%20ordered%20the%20filing%20of%20charges%20against%20eight%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshocks-3rd-degree-torture-cops-doctor-to-be-charged-for-custodial-death-6352178%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%203%20Friends%20Built%20Low-Cost%2C%20Eco-Toilets%20in%20a%20Rural%20Govt%20School%20in%20Just%201%20Month%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJust%20a%20while%20ago%2C%20students%20in%20the%20government%20school%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%99s%20Nellivasal%20village%20were%20forced%20to%20go%20out%20in%20the%20open%20for%20defecation.%20Without%20any%20proper%20toilet%20facility%2C%20they%20urinated%20at%20the%20corner%20of%20the%20campus%20building%20at%20night%2C%20creating%20a%20stench%20in%20the%20entire%20hostel%20block%20that%20made%20it%20unbearable%20to%20sit%20in%20the%20dining%20area%20of%20the%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocated%20in%20the%20hilly%20forest%20area%20of%20the%20Jawadhu%20Hills%20(Eastern%20Ghats)%20in%20Tirupathur%20district%2C%20the%20tribal%20village%20school%20lacked%20toilet%20facilities%2C%20owing%20to%20its%20remote%20location%20and%20financial%20constraints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20continued%20until%20architect%20Barnala%20Michael%20and%20a%20group%20of%20like-minded%20friends%20came%20together%20to%20solve%20the%20social%20issue%20through%20collective%20effort%20and%20crowdfunding.%20Keeping%20the%20constraints%20in%20mind%2C%20they%20adopted%20an%20unconventional%20design%20approach%20with%20unique%20toilet%20units%20and%20cost-effective%20construction%20methods%20and%20techniques.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20they%20constructed%20three%20toilets%20and%20an%20open%20bath%20area%20that%20cost%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20%E2%80%94%20a%2030%20percent%20reduction%20in%20total%20cost%20compared%20to%