heartbreaking%20news%20report%20about%20a%20young%20girl%20who%20tragically%20lost%20her%20life%20due%20to%20health%20complications%20from%20constipation%2C%20caused%20by%20the%20absence%20of%20toilets%20in%20her%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20disturbing%20incident%20propelled%20her%20into%20action.%20After%20initial%20discussions%20with%20her%20Facebook%20friend%2C%20Sivaraj%2C%20who%20runs%20Cuckoo%20Movement%20%E2%80%94%20a%20group%20of%20like-minded%20people%20and%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20together%2C%20they%20approached%20Michael%20to%20devise%20a%20plan%20to%20solve%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20us%20who%20were%20part%20of%20the%20project%20come%20from%20areas%20of%20water%20scarcity.%20We%20have%20known%20the%20issues%20of%20toilet%20facilities%20and%20the%20pain%20of%20open%20defecation.%20This%20problem%20aggravates%20during%20the%20rainy%20season.%20This%20was%20a%20common%20emotional%20pain%20point%2C%20which%20motivated%20us%20to%20come%20together%20to%20solve%20this%20problem%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Michael.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20dire%20situation%20where%20children%20were%20forced%20to%20defecate%20in%20the%20open%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20proper%20facilities%2C%20struck%20a%20chord%20with%20Sivaraj%20and%20Michael%20and%20led%20them%20to%20focus%20their%20efforts%20on%20the%20government%20school%20in%20Nellivasal%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reason%20why%20we%20chose%20to%20construct%20toilets%20in%20Nellivasal%20village%20was%20because%20of%20its%20difficult%20terrain%20where%20construction%20of%20toilets%20was%20challenging%20and%20school%20children%20were%20forced%20to%20defecate%20in%20the%20open.%20This%20could%20be%20a%20starting%20point%20and%20prove%20to%20be%20an%20example%20for%20other%20similar%20locations%2C%E2%80%9D%20Michael%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20team%20went%20to%20the%20government%20school%20in%20Nellivasal%2C%20they%20found%20a%20toilet%20was%20constructed%20on%20the%20premises%2C%20mainly%20used%20by%20the%20teachers%20and%20girls%20during%20school%20hours.%20However%2C%20Michael%20says%2C%20there%20was%20no%20toilet%20facility%20for%20hostellers.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20enquired%2C%20we%20got%20to%20know%20that%20the%20school%20had%20been%20trying%20to%20get%20funds%20for%20construction%20of%20toilets%20but%20they%20could%20not%20succeed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1723809500.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20team%20constructed%20three%20toilets%20and%20an%20open%20bath%20area%20at%20the%20school%20campus.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1723809500.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1723809500-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1723809500-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1723809500-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1723809500-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361655%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20team%20constructed%20three%20toilets%20and%20an%20open%20bath%20area%20at%20the%20school%20campus.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20sought%20permission%20from%20the%20forest%20department%20to%20construct%20low-cost%20and%20sustainable%20toilets%20for%20the%20school.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20given%20a%20month%E2%80%99s%20time.%20We%20found%20that%20mobilising%20construction%20materials%20and%20workers%20was%20difficult%20in%20the%20area.%20So%2C%20we%20needed%20to%20be%20smart%20in%20building%20toilets%20which%20will%20require%20less%20cost%2C%20time%2C%20and%20resources%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20project%20was%20entirely%20funded%20by%20volunteers%20of%20the%20Cuckoo%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20design%2C%20cost%2C%20technique%3A%20constructing%20unique%20toilets%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20preparing%20a%20rough%20design%20for%20toilets%20in%20October%202023%2C%20Michael%20and%20the%20team%20started%20constructing%20the%20toilets.%20They%20employed%20innovative%20construction%20techniques%2C%20opting%20for%20ferrocement%20structures%20to%20reduce%20costs%20and%20expedite%20the%20building%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFerrocement%20construction%20technique%20is%20a%20low-cost%20method%20that%20is%20less%20labour%20intensive.%20In%20this%2C%20reinforced%20cement%20is%20applied%20over%20a%20chicken%20metal%20mesh.%20Additionally%2C%20we%20used%20polycarbonate%20sheet%2C%20a%20translucent%20material%20that%20allows%20natural%20light%20and%20outside%20visibility%20that%20could%20enable%20students%20to%20feel%20slight%20resemblance%20with%20their%20old%20ways%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20also%20used%20a%20leech%20pit%20system%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F78181%2Fvideo-waterless-toilets-just-rural-india-needs%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DEco%2520sans%2520toilet%2520costs%2520about%2C%2527flush%2520out%2527%2520the%2520waste.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewaste%20management%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20turning%20human%20waste%20into%20natural%20manure%20for%20the%20school%E2%80%99s%20garden.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20system%2C%20two%20pits%20are%20connected%20to%20the%20toilet%20and%20they%20are%20built%20such%20that%20water%20gets%20drained%20through%20its%20walls%20and%20solid%20waste%20remains%20in%20the%20pit.%20When%20one%20pit%20gets%20filled%2C%20excreta%20is%20collected%20in%20the%20next%20pit.%20Meanwhile%2C%20solid%20waste%20in%20the%20former%20turns%20into%20manure%20in%20that%20period%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1_11zon-1723809723.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20construction%20of%20toilets%20has%20been%20extremely%20convenient%20for%20school%20children%2C%20especially%20hostellers.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1_11zon-1723809723.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1_11zon-1723809723-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1_11zon-1723809723-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1_11zon-1723809723-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-1_11zon-1723809723-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361657%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20construction%20of%20toilets%20has%20been%20extremely%20convenient%20for%20school%20children%2C%20especially%20hostellers.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMichael%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWater%20is%20the%20main%20medium%20for%20the%20growth%20of%20microbes.%20When%20you%20remove%20water%20from%20solid%20waste%2C%20it%20does%20not%20cause%20any%20bad%20smell.%20Pits%20that%20have%20porous%20walls%20permit%20the%20contents%20to%20seep%20into%20the%20ground.%20Sawdust%20is%20applied%20to%20arrest%20the%20bad%20smell%20and%20microbial%20growth.%20It%20is%20a%20sustainable%20and%20natural%20way%20of%20waste%20management.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20Michael%20says%20they%20have%20designed%20the%20toilets%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20draws%20the%20interest%20of%20students%20who%20were%20accustomed%20to%20open%20defecation.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20built%20toilets%20in%20oval%20round%20shapes%20and%20adorned%20with%20vibrant%20colours%20to%20attract%20the%20students%20to%20use%20the%20enclosed%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F102470%2Fcarambolim-goa-village-eco-friendly-toilets%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeco-friendly%20approach%20%3C%2Fa%3Enot%20only%20addressed%20hygiene%20concerns%20but%20also%20promoted%20sustainable%20practices%20within%20the%20community.%20The%20project%20was%20completed%20by%20November%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20their%20work%20was%20immediate%20and%20profound.%20The%20newly%20constructed%20toilets%20not%20only%20provided%20essential%20facilities%20but%20also%20triggered%20a%20behavioural%20change%20among%20the%20students.%20Currently%2C%20about%2080%20rural%20students%20are%20using%20these%20toilets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKalaiselvi%20(16)%2C%20a%20Class%2012%20student%20of%20the%20school%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%20when%20there%20were%20no%20toilets%2C%20I%20would%20face%20a%20lot%20of%20problems%2C%20especially%20during%20menstruation.%20Although%20we%20used%20the%20toilet%20meant%20for%20teachers%2C%20sometimes%20we%20had%20to%20go%20out%20in%20the%20open.%20These%20new%20toilets%20have%20brought%20immense%20comfort%20to%20us.%20I%20really%20like%20the%20structure%20of%20the%20toilets%20and%20also%20the%20paintings%20made%20on%20them!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Michael%20who%20visited%20the%20school%20a%20month%20back%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20the%20toilets%20were%20functioning%20properly.%20Now%2C%20there%20is%20no%20such%20issue%20of%20bad%20smell%20on%20campus%20and%20children%20are%20leading%20a%20regular%20school%20life.%20The%20improved%20sanitation%20conditions%20enhanced%20cleanliness%2C%20punctuality%2C%20and%20overall%20well-being%20of%20the%20school%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20hope%20that%20the%20idea%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F95712%2Fseva-mandir-rajasthan-ecosan-toilets%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeco-toilets%20%3C%2Fa%3Espreads%20to%20schools%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20where%20students%20lack%20access%20to%20toilets.%20With%20our%20example%2C%20we%20hope%20to%20inspire%20architects%2C%20engineers%2C%20school%20teachers%2C%20and%20government%20officials%20to%20provide%20dignity%20to%20our%20students%2C%20protect%20the%20environment%2C%20and%20embrace%20sustainability%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Prem%20Kumar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723818152000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftoilets-2-1723809641.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D361652%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Nellivasal%20village%2C%20students%20at%20a%20government%20school%20had%20to%20defecate%20in%20the%20open%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20proper%20toilets.%20Architect%20Barnala%20Michael%20along%20with%20his%20friends%20Vishnupriya%20and%20Sivaraj%20constructed%20low-cost%2C%20sustainable%20toilets%2C%20addressing%20hygiene%20issues%20and%20promoting%20eco-friendly%20practices.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F361652%2Feco-toilets-sustainable-low-cost-architect-barnala-michael-vishnupriya-sivaraj-govt-school-nellivasal-tamil-nadu%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Monkeypox%20Cases%20Rising%3A%20How%20Worried%20Should%20You%20Be%20-%2010%20Points%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhile%20usually%20mild%2C%20mpox%20can%20kill.%20Children%2C%20pregnant%20women%20and%20people%20with%20weakened%20immune%20systems%2C%20such%20as%20those%20with%20HIV%2C%20are%20all%20at%20higher%20risk%20of%20complications.%20The%20WHO%20declared%20the%20recent%20outbreak%20of%20the%20disease%20a%20public%20health%20emergency%20after%20a%20new%20offshoot%20of%20the%20mpox%20virus%2C%20first%20identified%20in%20Democratic%20Republic%20of%20Congo%2C%20began%20spreading%20to%20other%20neighbouring%20countries.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMpox%20transmits%20through%20close%20physical%20contact%2C%20including%20sexual%20contact%2C%20but%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20that%20it%20spreads%20easily%20through%20the%20air.%20The%20new%20offshoot%20has%20caused%20global%20alarm%20because%20it%20appears%20to%20spread%20more%20easily%20between%20people.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETwo%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20WHO%20declared%20mpox%20was%20an%20emergency%20when%20a%20form%20of%20the%20disease%2C%20'clade%20IIb'%2C%20began%20to%20spread%20globally%2C%20largely%20among%20men%20who%20have%20sex%20with%20men.%20That%20outbreak%20was%20brought%20under%20control%20after%20behaviour%20change%20and%20safe%20sex%20practices%2C%20plus%20vaccines%2C%20helped%20people%20at%20risk%20protect%20themselves%20in%20many%20countries.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBut%20mpox%20has%20been%20a%20public%20health%20problem%20in%20parts%20of%20Africa%20for%20decades.%20The%20first%20ever%20human%20case%20was%20in%20Congo%20in%201970%2C%20and%20it%20has%20had%20outbreaks%20ever%20since.%20The%20current%20outbreak%2C%20Congo's%20worst%20ever%2C%20has%20seen%2027%2C000%20cases%20and%20more%20than%201%2C100%20deaths%20since%20January%202023%2C%20largely%20among%20children.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETwo%20strains%20of%20mpox%20are%20now%20spreading%20in%20Congo%20-%20the%20endemic%20form%20of%20the%20virus%2C%20'clade%20I'%2C%20and%20a%20new%20offshoot%20called%20'clade%20Ib'%2C%20with%20the%20term%20'clade'%20referring%20to%20a%20form%20of%20the%20virus.%20The%20new%20offshoot%20has%20now%20moved%20from%20eastern%20Congo%20to%20Rwanda%2C%20Uganda%2C%20Burundi%20and%20Kenya.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESweden%20reported%20the%20first%20case%20of%20the%20new%20form%2C%20'clade%20Ib'%2C%20outside%20Africa%20on%20Thursday.%20A%20WHO%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20case%20reiterated%20the%20need%20for%20partnership%2C%20and%20the%20agency%20continues%20to%20advise%20against%20travel%20restrictions%20to%20stop%20the%20spread%20of%20mpox.%20Pakistan%20on%20Friday%20also%20confirmed%20a%20case%20of%20the%20mpox%20virus%20in%20a%20patient%20who%20had%20returned%20from%20a%20Gulf%20country%2C%20though%20it%20was%20unclear%20whether%20it%20was%20of%20the%20new%20variant%20or%20of%20the%20clade%20that%20has%20been%20spreading%20globally%20since%202022.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBut%20in%202022%2C%20a%20WHO%20appeal%20for%20%2434%20million%20to%20fight%20mpox%20got%20no%20take-up%20from%20donors%2C%20and%20there%20was%20huge%20inequity%20in%20who%20had%20access%20to%20vaccine%20doses.%20African%20countries%20had%20no%20access%20to%20the%20two%20shots%20used%20in%20the%20global%20outbreak%2C%20made%20by%20Bavarian%20Nordic%20and%20KM%20Biologics.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETwo%20years%20later%20that%20remains%20the%20case%2C%20although%20there%20are%20efforts%20to%20change%20that%2C%20the%20WHO%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20as%20it%20appealed%20for%20dose%20donations%20from%20countries%20with%20stockpiles.%20Africa%20CDC%20said%20it%20has%20a%20plan%20to%20secure%20doses%2C%20without%20elaborating%20further%2C%20but%20stocks%20are%20currently%20limited.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFatality%20rates%20vary%2C%20and%20depend%20heavily%20on%20the%20healthcare%20available%20to%20the%20sickest%20patients.%20In%20Congo%20in%20this%20outbreak%2C%20the%20rate%20across%20both%20'clade%20I'%20and%20'clade%20Ib'%20has%20been%20around%204%20per%20cent.%20'Clade%20II'%2C%20which%20spread%20globally%2C%20was%20much%20less%20deadly.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHowever%2C%20mpox%20is%20not%20COVID-19.%20There%20are%20tools%20that%20are%20proven%20to%20work%20to%20stop%20the%20spread%20and%20help%20those%20at%20risk%2C%20and%20it%20does%20not%20spread%20as%20easily.%20The%20challenge%20now%2C%20which%20the%20emergency%20declarations%20aim%20to%20highlight%2C%20is%20making%20sure%20those%20tools%20reach%20those%20who%20need%20them%20most%2C%20in%20Congo%20and%20neighbouring%20countries.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20Reuters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723817820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fa3vtg9j_mpox_625x300_16_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmonkeypox-cases-rising-how-worried-should-you-be-10-points-6352133%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20World%20Health%20Organization%20has%20declared%20that%20an%20outbreak%20of%20mpox%2C%20a%20viral%20infection%20that%20spreads%20through%20close%20contact%2C%20represents%20a%20global%20health%20emergency%20for%20the%20second%20time%20in%20two%20years.%20Mpox%20causes%20flu-like%20symptoms%20and%20pus-filled%20lesions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmonkeypox-cases-rising-how-worried-should-you-be-10-points-6352133%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gold%20loan%20demand%20stays%20strong%20despite%20cash%20disbursement%20curbs%3A%20CRISIL%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723817187000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-08%2F13%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1723567980-0121.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fn