er%20the%20Independence%20Day%20celebrations%20at%20Red%20Fort%2C%20where%20too%20the%20athletes%20were%20in%20attendance%20on%20Thursday.%20The%20video%20of%20the%20interaction%20was%20shared%20by%20Modi%20and%20the%20athletes%20could%20be%20seen%20having%20one-on-one%20chats%20with%20the%20PM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20such%20conversation%20with%20Lakshya%2C%20who%20finished%20fourth%20in%20the%20men's%20singles%20badminton%20competition%2C%20Modi%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20met%20Lakshya%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20he%20was%20very%20small%20but%20now%20he%20has%20grown%20up.%20Do%20you%20know%2C%20this%20time%20you%20have%20become%20a%20celebrity%3F%20To%20this%2C%20Lakshya%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BYes%20sir.%20But%20during%20matches%20Prakash%20Sir%20took%20my%20phone%20and%20told%20me%20till%20the%20matches%20are%20over%2C%20you%20won't%20get%20your%20phone.%20But%20after%20that%20I%20got%20to%20know%20the%20support%20I%20got.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20learning%20experience%20and%20little%20heart-breaking%20as%20well%20because%20I%20came%20so%20close%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%2022-year-old%20who%20lost%20from%20a%20position%20of%20strength%20in%20the%20bronze%20playoff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20laughing%20Modi%20instantly%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BPrakash%20Sir%20was%20so%20disciplined%20and%20strict%2C%20I%20will%20send%20him%20the%20next%20time%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%20The%20Paris%20Olympics%20were%20promoted%20as%20eco-friendly%20Games.%20So%2C%20there%20were%20no%20air%20conditioners%20in%20any%20rooms%20in%20the%20Games%20village%2C%20forcing%20the%20sports%20ministry%20to%20dispatch%2040%20portable%20ACs%20on%20an%20urgent%20basis%20for%20their%20comfortable%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20laughing%20Modi%20asked%20all%20the%20athletes%20who%20all%20cursed%20him%20for%20the%20situation%2C%20to%20which%20no%20one%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20no%20ACs%20and%20it%20was%20hot%20as%20well%2C%20so%20I%20want%20to%20know%20which%20of%20you%20cried%20first%20saying%20'Modi%20speaks%20big%20but%20there%20are%20no%20ACs%20in%20rooms%20so%20what%20should%20we%20do'%2C%26quot%3B%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWho%20all%20are%20there%20who%20faced%20most%20difficulties%3F%20But%20when%20I%20learnt%20that%2C%20within%20a%20few%20hours%20that%20work%20also%20was%20done.%20See%20how%20we%20try%20to%20provide%20you%20the%20best%20of%20facilities%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EParis%20didn't%20gave%20ACs%20to%20olympic%20players.%20You%20must%20have%20thought%20what%20Modi%20has%20done%20but%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20came%20to%20know%2C%20ACs%20were%20arranged%20for%20each%20and%20every%20player%20within%20hours%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FILPGnGLTVT%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FILPGnGLTVT%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20(%40kanchandwivedi3)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkanchandwivedi3%2Fstatus%2F1824378969593954701%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2016%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20also%20had%20a%20light-hearted%20chat%20with%20Harmanpreet%2C%20who%20opened%20up%20on%20how%20the%20team%20fought%20back%20after%20being%20down%20to%2010%20men%20for%20more%20than%2040%20minutes%20in%20the%20quarterfinal%20against%20Great%20Britain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20tell%20me%20when%20you%20to%20fight%20with%2010-men%20against%20Britain%2C%20you%20must%20have%20been%20demoralised%20from%20the%20start%2C%20Sarpanch%20saab%2C%20please%20tell%2C%20it%20was%20very%20difficult%2C%26quot%3B%20Modi%20asked%20the%20India%20captain%2C%20addressing%20him%20with%20his%20nickname.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarmanpreet%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BYes%20Sir%2C%20it%20was%20very%20difficult%20because%20we%20got%20the%20red%20card%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20but%20our%20coaching%20staff%20helped%20us%20a%20lot.%20We%20visualised%20every%20situation%20because%20in%20Olympics%20anything%20can%20happen.%20The%20motivation%20of%20the%20team%20also%20increased%20because%20we%20have%20a%20rivalry%20with%20GB%20(Britain).%26quot%3B%20Modi%20interrupted%20and%20laughingly%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20going%20on%20for%20the%20last%20150%20years.%26quot%3B%20Harmanpreet%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20fought%20and%20ended%20the%20match%201-1%20and%20won%20it%20in%20shoot-out.%20It%20never%20ever%20happened%20in%20Olympics%20history%20(playing%20with%2010%20men%20for%2042%20minutes%20and%20then%20winning).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EParis%20Olympics%20launch-pad%20for%20Indian%20sports'%20rise%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20believes%20the%20just-concluded%20Paris%20Olympics%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20turning%20point%20for%20India.%20The%20117-member%20Indian%20contingent%20returned%20with%20six%20medals%2C%20including%20one%20silver%20and%20five%20bronze.%20The%20count%20was%20one%20less%20than%20Tokyo%20and%20there%20was%20no%20gold%20in%20the%20tally%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Modi%20appreciated%20the%20efforts%20of%20all%20athletes%20who%20represented%20the%20country%20and%20said%20their%20inputs%20will%20help%20in%20successfully%20getting%20the%20hosting%20rights%20of%20the%202036%20Games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20who%20have%20returned%20after%20losing%2C%20please%20get%20this%20out%20of%20your%20mind.%20You%20made%20the%20country%20proud%20and%20came%20back%20after%20learning%20something.%20Sports%20is%20one%20area%20where%20no%20one%20loses%2C%20everybody%20learns%2C%26quot%3B%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20Paris%20Olympics%20will%20be%20a%20launch-pad%20for%20the%20rise%20of%20Indian%20sports.%20This%20is%20going%20to%20be%20our%20turning%20point.%20After%20that%20there%20will%20only%20be%20wins.%20We%20are%20not%20going%20to%20stop%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20termed%20the%20athletes%20as%20%26quot%3BIndia's%20soldiers%20of%202036%20Olympics%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20preparing%20to%20host%20the%202036%20Olympics.%20In%20this%20case%20many%20athletes%20who%20played%20in%20the%20Olympics%2C%20their%20inputs%20are%20very%20important.%20You%20might%20have%20observed%20many%20things%20there%2C%20from%20Olympics%20planning%20to%20all%20facilities%2C%20from%20sports%20management%20to%20event%20management%2C%26quot%3B%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20experiences%2C%20your%20observations%2C%20we%20need%20to%20write%20them%20down%2C%20so%20in%202036%20Olympics%20all%20the%20little%20things%20and%20experiences%20of%20yours%20will%20help%20us%20in%20preparing%20for%20the%20Games.%20In%20one%20way%20you%20are%20soldiers%20of%202036%20Olympics%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723815000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Ftseshpfs_narendra-modi_625x300_15_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fwho-all-cursed-me-for-lack-of-acs-in-paris-pm-narendra-modi-shares-a-laugh-with-indias-olympics-2024-stars-6349289%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20termed%20the%20athletes%20as%20%26quot%3BIndia's%20soldiers%20of%202036%20Olympics%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fwho-all-cursed-me-for-lack-of-acs-in-paris-pm-narendra-modi-shares-a-laugh-with-indias-olympics-2024-stars-6349289%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ashok%20Leyland%20sees%20high%20enquiry%20from