0Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fdugdl13_legacy-media_625x300_16_August_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20again%2C%20social%20media%20has%20reminded%20the%20editors%20and%20managers%20of%20traditional%20media%20that%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20live%20events%20or%20disseminating%20news%20worldwide%20in%20real%20time%2C%20they%20cannot%20compete.%20While%20traditional%20media%20was%20squabbling%20over%20whether%20the%20live%20interaction%20on%20X%20between%20tech%20billionaire%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20Grand%20Old%20Party%20(GOP)%20nominee%20Donald%20Trump%20was%20a%20conversation%2C%20a%20conversational%20interview%20or%20an%20interview%2C%20the%20chat%20between%20the%20world's%20two%20most%20unavoidable%20men%20crossed%20200%20million%20views%2C%20as%20per%20Musk's%20claim%20in%20a%20post.%20The%20morning%20after%2C%20Musk%20tweeted%20again%2C%20saying%20the%20conversation%20had%20garnered%20one%20billion%20combined%20views%20-%20a%20jaw-dropping%20number%20for%20legacy%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20keeping%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20the%20event's%20coverage%20by%20traditional%20media.%20It%20was%20disappointing%20to%20see%20that%20much%20of%20it%20was%20mostly%20negative%3B%20the%20slew%20of%20headlines%20both%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20the%20US%20painted%20the%20two-hour%20interaction%20in%20a%20dark%20light.%20One%20headline%20screamed%3A%20%26quot%3BTrump's%20interview%20with%20Musk%20devolves%20into%20yet%20another%20X%20catastrophe%26quot%3B.%20Legacy%20print%20media%20published%20a%20number%20of%20articles%20on%20the%20event.%20%3Cem%3EUSA%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%20it%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Bunmitigated%20disaster%26quot%3B%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Btwo-hour%20ramble%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecalled%20it%20%26quot%3Bsoftballs%26quot%3B.%20Other%20traditional%20media%20outlets%20were%20no%20different%3A%20%3Cem%3ECNN%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecompared%20the%20event%20to%20watching%20%26quot%3BGrumpy%20Old%20Men%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3EMSNBC%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecalled%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bfailed%26quot%3B%20interview.%20Some%20focused%20more%20on%20the%20delay%20caused%20by%20a%20technical%20glitch.%20A%20%3Cem%3EGuardian%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0analysis%20was%20headlined%3A%20%26quot%3BElon%20Musk's%20X%20suffers%20tech%20failure%20at%20start%20of%20Donald%20Trump%20interview%26quot%3B%2C%20while%20BBC%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMusk's%20X%20talk%20with%20Trump%20hit%20by%20tech%20glitches%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUK%20Riots%20And%20Social%20Media%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20hours%20after%20three%20young%20girls%20were%20brutally%20stabbed%20to%20death%20in%20the%20UK's%20Southport%20town%20on%20July%2029%2C%20news%20and%20reactions%20began%20to%20flow%20on%20social%20platforms%2C%20such%20as%20TikTok%2C%20Instagram%2C%20Facebook%20and%20YouTube.%20There%20were%20real-time%20updates%20on%20the%20horrific%20incident%20on%20these%20platforms.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20many%20felt%20that%20the%20mainstream%20media%20offered%20a%20lukewarm%20coverage%20of%20the%20incident%20until%20all%20hell%20broke%20loose%20and%20widespread%20violent%20protests%20swept%20across%20towns%20and%20cities%20in%20England.%20The%20news%20of%20the%20three%20girls%20being%20killed%20was%20initially%20treated%20by%20the%20legacy%20media%20as%20a%20routine%20crime%20story%20after%20it%20emerged%20that%20there%20was%20no%20terror%20link.%20It%20was%20only%20after%20fake%20videos%20and%20unverified%20news%20began%20circulating%20widely%20and%20getting%20millions%20of%20views%20that%20established%20media%20woke%20up%20from%20its%20slumber.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vacuum%20was%20filled%20by%20some%20notorious%20far-right%20people%20on%20social%20media%20who%20were%20accused%20of%20posting%20inflammatory%20material.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20government%20named%20Elon%20Musk%20as%20one%20of%20those%20who%20were%20%26quot%3Bstirring%20the%20pot%26quot%3B.%20Reacting%20to%20the%20riots%2C%20Musk%20suggested%20in%20a%20post%20that%20%26quot%3Bcivil%20war%20is%20inevitable%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20UK.%20Responding%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Keith%20Starmer's%20comments%20on%20the%20attacks%20on%20the%20Muslim%20community%20he%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BShouldn't%20you%20be%20concerned%20about%20attacks%20on%20all%20communities%3F%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20accused%20the%20police%20of%20being%20biased%20against%20protesters%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBillionaire%20Knows%20What%20He's%20Doing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%20appears%20to%20have%20learnt%20something%20from%20the%20fall%20of%20traditional%20media%2C%20which%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20lacking%20in%20innovation%20and%20stagnating%3B%20it%20desperately%20depends%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%20to%20amplify%20its%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20194.4%20million%20followers%20on%20X.%20He%20is%20the%20most%20followed%20man%20on%20the%20platform.%20The%20CEO%20of%20X%2C%20Linda%20Yaccarini%2C%20says%20the%20platform%20has%20500%20million%20active%20users%20a%20month.%20Surely%2C%20Musk%20is%20aware%20of%20this%20reach%2C%20and%20he%20is%20using%20it%20strategically%20to%20his%20advantage%20with%20a%20view%20to%20weaken%20the%20legacy%20media.%20One%20can%20see%20his%20strategy%20at%20play%20by%20the%20way%20he%20was%20able%20to%20pull%20off%20a%20two-hour%20interview%20with%20Trump%20and%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20it%20how%20he%20drummed%20it%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20not%20an%20isolated%20incident.%20Musk%20came%20to%20Donald%20Trump's%20defence%20in%20March%20too%20when%20the%20latter%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Ohio%20that%20there%20would%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bblood%20bath%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20US%20if%20he%20lost%20the%20November%20election.%20He%20fired%20a%20series%20of%20posts%20on%20X%20in%20response%20to%20the%20coverage%20and%20urged%20the%20people%20to%20use%20his%20platform%20to%20share%20news%20instead%20of%20reading%20or%20watching%20it%20on%20traditional%20outlets.%20He%20accused%20the%20legacy%20media%20of%20lying%20about%20Trump's%20comment%2C%20saying%20his%20comment%20was%20taken%20out%20of%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpen%20Challenge%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%2C%20described%20variously%20as%20a%20genius%20and%20innovator%2C%20besides%20being%20one%20of%20the%20richest%20men%20in%20the%20world%2C%20appears%20to%20have%20openly%20challenged%20the%20traditional%20media's%20established%20200-year%20hegemony%20over%20news%20and%20current%20affairs.%20In%20one%20of%20his%20posts%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCitizen%20journalism%20from%20actual%20domain%20experts%20and%20people%20actually%20on%20the%20ground%20is%20much%20faster%2C%20more%20accurate%20and%20has%20less%20bias%20than%20the%20legacy%20media%26quot%3B.%20The%20claim%20of%20being%20%26quot%3Bmore%20accurate%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bless%20biased%26quot%3B%20can%20be%20contested%2C%20but%20not%20social%20media%20being%20%26quot%3Bmuch%20faster%26quot%3B%20than%20the%20legacy%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20platforms%2C%20such%20as%20%C2%A0TikTok%2C%20YouTube%2C%20Instagram%20and%20Facebook%2C%20are%20officially%20still%20tech%20companies%2C%20but%20they%20have%20daily%20news%20capsules%2C%20real-time%20coverage%20of%20events%20and%20timeline%20postings%2C%20which%20cannot%20be%20matched%20by%20mainstream%20media.%20These%20have%20emerged%20as%20a%20big%20challenge%20to%20the%20established%2C%20legacy%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeedless%20to%20say%2C%20many%20political%20parties%20and%20popular%20leaders%20of%20the%20world%20have%20robust%20social%20media%20strategies.%20They%20too%20have%20grasped%20the%20importance%20of%20speed%20and%20reach%20and%20often%20bypass%20the%20legacy%20media%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20their%20followers%20and%20voters%20of%20their%20countries%2C%20because%20they%20believe%20they%20interact%20more%20closely%20with%20their%20supporters%20through%20these%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20Legislation%20Help%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEurope%20has%20already%20passed%20a%20law%20to%20hold%20social%20media%20accountable.%20Now%20it's%20the%20British%20government's%20turn.%20Its%20Online%20Safety%20Bill%20aims%20to%20regulate%20social%20media%20platforms%20and%20protect%20users%20from%20harmful%20content.%20The%20Bill%20asks%20companies%20to%20remove%20fake%20and%20illegal%20content%20and%20establishes%20Ofcom%20(media%20regulators)%20as%20the%20regulator%20with%20the%20power%20to%20fine%20companies%20up%20to%20%C2%A318%20million%20or%2010%25%20of%20annual%20global%20turnover%20for%20non-compliance.%20The%20legislation%20is%20expected%20to%20come%20into%20force%20by%202025.%20Some%20anti-far-right%20organisations%20have%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20implement%20it%20as%20early%20as%20possible.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20will%20that%20in%20some%20way%20curb%20the%20growing%20popularity%20of%20social%20media%3F%20Will%20it%20slow%20them%20down%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20speed%20with%20which%20they%20churn%20out%20news%3F%20Will%20the%20erosion%20of%20trust%20and%20threat%20to%20democracy%20argument%20hold%20good%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Should%20The%20Legacy%20Media%20Do%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20can%20say%20with%20the%20authority%20of%20my%2030%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20mainstream%20Western%20media%20that%20they%20are%20still%20slow%20to%20innovate%2C%20as%20they%20were%20slow%20to%20embrace%20digital%20transformation%20and%20shy%20of%20collaborating%20with%20social%20media.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDigital%20transformation%26quot%3B%20is%20the%20buzzword%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%20%3C%2Fem%3Etoday.%20They%20are%20being%20bold%20in%20their%20leap%20to%20digitisation%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20traditional%20media%2C%20such%20as%20TV%20and%20radio.%20Also%2C%20it%20may%20sound%20bizarre%2C%20but%20%3Cem%3EBBC%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20quite%20new%20to%20TikTok.%20It%20dawned%20on%20them%20only%20last%20year%20that%20they%20had%20lost%20out%20on%20the%20young%20audiences%20of%20TikTok%20who%2C%20they%20learnt%2C%20consumed%20news%20in%20bulk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20a%20strategy%20full%20of%20risks.%20A%20balance%20between%20legacy%20and%20social%20media%2C%20along%20with%20innovation%20and%20speed%2C%20could%20be%20the%20key%20to%20surviving%20and%20staying%20stable.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Syed%20Zubair%20Ahmed%20is%20a%20London-based%20senior%20Indian%20journalist%20with%20three%20decades%20of%20experience%20with%20the%20Western%20media)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723813500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fvnmuu468_legacy-media_625x300_16_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ftrump-musk-chat-shows-innovation-alone-can-save-legacy-media-6351520%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20traditional%20media%20was%20squabbling%20over%20whether%20the%20live%20interaction%20between%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20Donald%20Trump%20was%20a%20conversation%2C%20a%20conversational%20interview%20or%20an%20interview%2C%20the%20chat%20crossed%20200%20million%20views%2C%20and%201%20billion%20by%20the%20next%20morning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ftrump-musk-chat-shows-innovation-alone-can-save-legacy-media-6351520%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20India-Bangladesh%20Border%2C%20A%20Strip%20Of%20Land%20Where%20Laws%20Of%20Both%20Apply%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20border%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%2C%20a%20country%20which%20is%20slowly%20emerging%20from%20a%20period%20of%20violence%20and%20turmoil%2C%20lies%20a%20narrow%2C%20unique%20strip%20of%20land%20where%20people%20can%20move%20freely%20without%20passports%20and%20visas%2C%20and%20where%20the%20laws%20of%20both%20countries%20apply.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Teen%20Bigha%20Corridor%2C%20in%20West%20Bengal's%20Cooch%20Behar%2C%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20handed%20over%20to%20Bangladesh%20in%201974.%20As%20part%20of%20a%20treaty%20between%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20her%20Bangladeshi%20counterpart%20Mujibur%20Rahman%2C%20India%20was%20to%20hand%20over%20sovereignty%20of%20the%20Teen%20Bigha%20Corridor%20to%20Bangladesh%20and%20get%20South%20Berubari%20in%20return.%20This%20was%20intended%20to%20facilitate%20Bangladesh's%20access%20to%20the%20Dahargram-Angarpota%20enclaves%20and%2C%20for%20India%2C%20to%20the%20enclaves%20near%20South%20Berubari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Bangladesh%20held%20up%20its%20end%20of%20the%20deal%2C%20India%20couldn't%20do%20so%20because%20a%20constitutional%20amendment%20would%20be%20required.%20A%20compromise%20was%20found%20in%201992%20and%20the%20Teen%20Bigha%20Corridor%20was%20leased%20to%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20created%20a%20unique%20situation%20where%20the%20strip%20of%20land%20sees%20Bangladeshi%20citizens%20entering%20Indian%20soil%20and%20then%20returning%20to%20their%20country%20without%20a%20visa%20or%20passport.%20Under%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20agreement%2C%20Bangladeshis%20passing%20through%20the%20corridor%20are%20not%20frisked%20and%20there%20is%20no%20checking%20that%20takes%20place.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20an%20intersection%20through%20which%20traffic%20from%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20flow%20%C2%A0-%20east%20to%20west%20for%20Bangladesh%20and%20north%20to%20south%20for%20India%20%C2%A0-%20and%20that%20is%20a%20space%20where%20the%20laws%20of%20both%20countries%20apply.%20If%20an%20Indian%20violates%20any%20rules%2C%20Indian%20law%20will%20apply%20to%20him%20and%2C%20similarly%2C%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20under%20Bangladeshi%20law%20for%20a%20citizen%20from%20that%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strip%20of%20land%20is%20manned%20both%20by%20the%20Indian%20Border%20Security%20Force%20(BSF)%20and%20the%20Border%20Guard%2C%20Bangladesh.%20The%20flow%20of%20traffic%20is%20regulated%20by%20policemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bangladeshi%20enclave%20that%20the%20corridor%20leads%20to%20has%20an%20area%20of%2019%20square%20kilometres%20and%20is%20surrounded%20by%20India%20on%20all%20sides.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBangladesh%20At%20A%20Crossroads%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangladesh%20now%20has%20an%20interim%20government%2C%20led%20by%20Nobel%20laureate%20Muhammad%20Yunus%2C%20after%20widespread%20protests%20forced%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20to%20resign%20as%20prime%20minister%20and%20flee%20to%20India%20on%20August%205.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20450%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20since%20the%20latest%20wave%20of%20protests%20began%20in%20June%20and%20there%20have%20been%20reports%20of%20minorities%20being%20targeted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yunus%20spoke%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Friday%20and%20assured%20him%20that%20the%20interim%20government%20will%20protect%20Hindus%20and%20other%20minority%20communities%20in%20Bangladesh%20and%20ensure%20their%20safety%20and%20security.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReceived%20a%20telephone%20call%20from%20Professor%20Muhammad%20Yunus.%20Exchanged%20views%20on%20the%20prevailing%20situation.%20Reiterated%20India's%20support%20for%20a%20democratic%2C%20stable%2C%20peaceful%20and%20progressive%20Bangladesh.%20He%20assured%20protection%2C%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20Hindus%20and%20all%20minorities%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723812240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fpdnifeig_teen-bigha-corridor_625x300_16_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-india-bangladesh-border-a-strip-of-land-where-laws-of-both-apply-6351429%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20the%20border%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%2C%20a%20country%20which%20is%20slowly%20emerging%20from%20a%20period%20of%20violence%20and%20turmoil%2C%20lies%20a%20narrow%2C%20unique%20strip%20of%20land%20where%20the%20laws%20of%20both%20countries%20apply%2F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-india-bangladesh-border-a-strip-of-land-where-laws-of-both-apply-6351429%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22JSW%20Cement%20files%20draft%20papers%20with%20Sebi%20to%20raise%20Rs%204%2C000%20crore%20via%20IPO%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723811715000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-05%2F02%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1714669756-0508.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fipo%2Fjsw-cement-files-draft-papers-with-sebi-to-raise-rs-4-000-crore-via-ipo-124081601380_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22JSW%20Cement's%20IPO%20will%20hit%20the%20market%20while%20its%20other%20listed%20competitors%20are%20in%20a%20frenzy%20to%20increase%20capacity%20and%20gain%20market%20share%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fipo%2Fjsw-cement-files-draft-papers-with-sebi-to-raise-rs-4-000-crore-via-ipo-124081601380_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fipo%2Fjsw-cement-files-draft