0the%20parliamentary%20elections%2C%20so%20we%20are%20not%20delayed%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20special%20status%20was%20revoked%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20government%20in%202019%20and%20the%20state%20was%20split%20into%20two%20federally-administered%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%209%20million%20people%20are%20registered%20to%20vote%20for%20the%2090-member%20legislative%20assembly%2C%20the%20election%20panel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20territory%20recorded%20its%20highest%20turnout%20of%2058.46%25%20in%2035%20years%20in%20parliamentary%20elections%20held%20in%20April%20and%20May%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20government%20and%20election%20officials%20said%20this%20reflected%20the%20faith%20of%20Kashmir's%20voters%20in%20the%20democratic%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20an%20uptick%20in%20the%20terror-related%20incidents%20in%20the%20recent%20past%2C%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSecurity%20threats%20to%20candidates%20will%20be%20thoroughly%20under%20the%20radar%20of%20the%20establishment%20and%20will%20be%20taken%20care%20of.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20festival%20season%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%20There%20is%20season%20of%20apple.%20Of%20Jasmine.%20Of%20Saffron.%20There%20are%20shikaras%20and%20tulips.%20There%20is%20a%20Gurez%20festival%20also.%20All%20these%20things%20have%20come%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20top%20poll%20officer%2C%20underlining%20that%20the%20time%20is%20right%20for%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723807380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fi79bl3kg_cec-rajiv-kumar-_625x300_16_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjammu-and-kashmir-poll-dates-going-past-top-court-deadline-election-body-chief-responds-6350799%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20is%20no%