n%20has%20rejuvenated%2040%20wells%20and%20six%20lakes%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20Pune.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFast%20forward%20to%202024%2C%20people%20are%20now%20using%20air%20conditioners%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20which%20never%20had%20such%20harsh%20summers%20before%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%20with%20a%20sigh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20this%20up%20as%20his%20responsibility%2C%20Kapil%20started%20%E2%80%98SayTrees%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20non-profit%20organisation%20dedicated%20to%20creating%20urban%20and%20rural%20forests%2C%20and%20rejuvenating%20lakes%20with%20support%20from%20corporations%20and%20the%20community.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20non-profit%20has%20planted%203.8%20million%20trees%20across%20the%20country%20and%20rejuvenated%20six%20lakes%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20sat%20down%20with%20the%20founder%20to%20learn%20how%20he%20has%20achieved%20this%20feat%20through%20community%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETo%20revive%20Bengaluru%20to%20its%20initial%20glory%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20in%20detail%20about%20his%20motivation%20to%20start%20SayTrees%2C%20the%20software%20engineer%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20moved%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20roads%20were%20covered%20with%20giant%20trees.%20The%20cover%20was%20so%20dense%20that%20one%20could%20not%20see%20the%20sun.%20One%20day%20when%20I%20was%20travelling%20from%20home%20to%20office%2C%20I%20was%20as%20usual%20looking%20at%20the%20tall%20trees%20on%20the%20roads.%20The%20other%20morning%2C%20I%20saw%20that%20all%20those%20trees%20were%20gone.%20It%20was%20disheartening%20for%20me%20as%20I%20valued%20them%20so%20much%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20trees%20were%20being%20chopped%20down%20for%20road%20widening%20and%20metro%20construction.%20Although%20the%20Government%20was%20transplanting%20them%2C%20I%20felt%20responsible%20as%20a%20citizen.%20Otherwise%2C%20Bengaluru%2