ags%2C%20we%20were%20using%20plastic%20bags.%20Later%20on%2C%20we%20also%20tried%20other%20sustainable%20bags%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20they%20were%20neither%20food%20grade%20quality%20nor%20superior.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20times%2C%20the%20customers%20would%20complain%20to%20us%20if%20some%20sharp%20bones%20would%20pop%20out%20from%20low-grade%20bags.%20However%2C%20Bio%20Reform%20bags%20meet%20all%20our%20requirements%20and%20can%20be%20easily%20sealed%20as%20well%2C%20similar%20to%20plastic.%20Besides%2C%20there%20was%20not%20much%20difference%20from%20the%20price%C2%A0%20point%20also.%20The%20plastic%20bags%20would%20cost%20us%20Rs%20160%20per%20kg%20whereas%20Bio%20Reform%20bags%20cost%20Rs%20180%20per%20kg%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20individual%20level%2C%20Azhar%20says%20that%20he%20has%20spearheaded%20a%20movement%20towards%20India%E2%80%99s%20vision%20to%20become%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F289750%2Findia-bans-single-use-plastics-eco-friendly-alternatives-cups-cutlery%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esingle-use%20plastic%3C%2Fa%3E-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIssues%20related%20to%20plastic%20pollution%20are%20not%20limited%20to%20affecting%20aquatic%20life%20and%20animals%20anymore.%20Today%2C%20microplastic%20has%20reached%20our%20bloodstream.%20Bottled%20water%20contains%20microplastics.%20Addressing%20this%20is%20an%20important%20and%20urgent%20problem%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20glad%20I%20am%20able%20to%20contribute%20my%20part.%20It%20is%20sometimes%20taxing%20to%20not%20lead%20a%20regular%20college%20life%20but%20in%20the%20end%2C%20it%20is%20all%20worth%20it.%20I%20feel%20content%20when%20I%20go%20back%20to%20sleep.%20But%20much%20more%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20to%20make%20India%20plastic-free%2C%20and%20I%20will%20continue%20to%20strive%20for%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3