n%20without%20challenges.%20However%2C%20the%20key%20lies%20in%20implementing%20measurable%20changes%20at%20every%20stage%20of%20operation%2C%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20the%20%E2%80%98Nirmal%20Sustainability%20Program%E2%80%99%20steps%20in.%20The%20initiative%20is%20thoughtfully%20designed%20and%20catalyses%20Merino%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20becoming%20a%20sustainable%20and%20responsible%20industry.%20The%20programme%20hinges%20on%20scaling%20business%20growth%20alongside%20societal%20prosperity%20and%20pro-environmental%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20laser%20focus%20on%20increased%20utilisation%20of%20green%20energy%2C%20water%20conservation%2C%20air%20pollution%20reduction%2C%20circular%20economy%2C%20waste%20recycling%2C%20large-scale%20plantation%2C%20and%20the%20implementation%20of%20organic%20manure%20in%20agro-farming%2C%20the%20company%20is%20attempting%20to%20achieve%20the%20overarching%20goal%20of%20continuously%20reducing%20its%20carbon%20footprint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20commitment%20to%20eco-consciousness%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMerino%20strives%20that%20wealth%20is%20generated%20with%20minimalistic%20harm%20to%20the%20environment.%20To%20understand%20how%20it%20is%20achieving%20this%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20take%20a%20look%20at%20its%20%E2%80%98Triple%20Bottom%20Line%20Framework%E2%80%99%20that%20encompasses%20three%20key%20dimensions%20%E2%80%94%20Environmental%2C%20Social%2C%20and%20Financial%20impacts.%20Success%20follows%20when%20each%20parameter%20is%20scaled%20in%20parallel%20to%20the%20other.%20Excellence%20lies%20at%20the%20convergence%20of%20economy%20and%20sustainability%2C%20they%20believe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-1723194040.jpg%5C%22