2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20spot%20provides%20a%20safe%20haven%20from%20larger%20predators%20like%20vultures%20and%20eagles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20many%20larger%20caf%C3%A9s%2C%20this%20one%20does%20not%20rely%20on%20genset%20generators%20for%20backup%20power.%20The%20reason%20is%20that%20these%20generators%20produce%20a%20humming%20noise%20that%20can%20disturb%20the%20local%20birdlife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLiving%20in%20a%20forest%2C%20our%20primary%20responsibility%20is%20to%20the%20birds%2C%20leopards%2C%20mountain%20goats%2C%20wild%20boars%2C%20and%20other%20wildlife%20that%20call%20this%20place%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20Amit%20explains.%20To%20protect%20the%20surrounding%20animals%2C%20they%20keep%20the%20caf%C3%A9%E2%80%99s%20lighting%20dim%20and%20the%20music%20at%20a%20low%20volume.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20their%20offerings%2C%20the%20couple%20leads%20tourists%20to%20unexplored%20spots%20such%20as%20the%20Kalagarh%20forest.%20They%20offer%20stays%20in%20forest%20bungalows%2C%20equipping%20them%20with%20lanterns%20and%20camping%20chairs%20as%20many%20lack%20electricity.%20They%20also%20arrange%20for%20guests%20to%20dine%20at%20local%20homes%2C%20thanks%20to%20their%20connection%20with%20residents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20something%20they%20really%20enjoy%20and%20adds%20an%20authentic%20touch%20to%20their%20experience%2C%E2%80%9D%20Amit%20notes.%20They%20also%20introduce%20guests%20to%20forest%20guards%20who%20live%20in%20isolation%20and%20rarely%20interact%20with%20outsiders.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20guards%20are%20always%20delighted%20to%20meet%20new%20people%20and%20have%20many%20stories%20to%20share%2C%E2%80%9D%20Amit%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caf%C3%A9%20created%20by%20Amit%20and%20Shipra%20was%20the%20first%20of%20its%20kind%20in%20Kalagarh%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359311%2Fchavni-maratha-camp-lohagad-visapur-fort-pune-maharasht