elhi-resident-turns-blue-book-victorian-era-bungalow-into-heritage-sustainable-hotel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echunk%20of%20history%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20open%20your%20eyes%2C%20your%20gaze%20will%20naturally%20fall%20upon%20the%20horizon%20where%20the%20Satavahana%20Caves%20%E2%80%94%20the%20oldest%20group%20of%20caves%20dating%20to%20the%20first%20century%20BCE%20%E2%80%94%20stand.%20Much%20of%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20history%20was%20shaped%20during%20these%20pre-colonial%20times%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F162931%2Fmumbai-pune-peshwa-british-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunder%20the%20Maratha%20reign%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20sounds%20of%20the%20past%20had%20to%20accompany%20the%20visualisation%20you%20just%20did%2C%20there%20would%20be%20the%20steady%20clippity-clop%20of%20horses%20as%20their%20master%20soldiers%20nudged%20them%20to%20go%20faster.%20The%20horses%20were%20a%20prelude%20to%20the%20liveried%20chariots%20that%20followed%20behind%20them%20carrying%20wealthy%20families%20and%20merchants%2C%20while%20bullock%20carts%20were%20designated%20to%20bear%20the%20brunt%20of%20the%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fmaratha-heritage-1-1722864134.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20tents%2C%20wadas%2C%20and%20royal%20carts%2C%20Chavni%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20Maratha%20era%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fmaratha-heritage-1-1722864134.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fmaratha-heritage-1-1722864134-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fmaratha-heritage-1-1722864134-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fmaratha-heritage-1-1722864134-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fmaratha-heritage-1-1722864134-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359855%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20tents%2C%20%3Cem%3Ewadas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20royal%20carts%2C%20Chavni%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20Maratha%20era%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Karlekar%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20important%20enjoyed%20these%20privileges%2C%20ordinary%20people%20would%20walk%20on%20foot.%20But%20providing%20some%20respite%20to%20them%20were%20the%20%3Cem%3Echavnis%20%3C%2Fem%3E(transit%20camps).%20These%20served%20as%20shelters%20for%20the%20troops%20and%20traders%20for%20when%20night%20fell%20or%20when%20they%20needed%20rest.%20It%20was%20during%20their%20travels%20from%20one%20place%20to%20the%20next%20that%20the%20Marathas%20spent%20a%20substantial%20chunk%20of%20their%20time%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%201600s%2C%20an%20observer%20looking%20from%20the%20top%20of%20the%20Lohagad%20fort%20would%20be%20privy%20to%20a%20beautiful%20scene%20of%20these%20caravans%20spinning%20a%20colossal%20web%20across%20the%20terrain.%20There%20was%20no%20denying%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3Echavnis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eheld%20a%20certain%20mystique.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20destination%20was%20sometimes%20uncertain%20but%20as%20food%20was%20cooked%20and%20jokes%20shared%2C%20some%20of%20the%20most%20beautiful%20friendships%20were%20struck.%20The%20desire%20to%20recreate%20those%20experiences%20in%20the%20present%20day%20is%20what%20compelled%20Karlekar%20and%20Shetye%20to%20set%20their%20eyes%20on%20this%20piece%20of%20land%20in%202017.%20And%20in%202019%2C%20the%20work%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20design%20process%2C%20the%20guiding%20script%20was%20to%20build%20a%20space%20that%20was%20rooted%20in%20Indianness%2C%20says%20Shetye.%20%E2%80%9CChavni%20is%20a%20concept%20that%20subtly%20nurtures%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20architectural%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F119761%2Fqueen-ahilyabai-holkar-maratha%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecultural%20legacy%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20does%20this%20while%20offering%20a%20tangible%20framework%20for%20the%20hospitality%20and%20tourism%20industry%20in%20Maharashtra.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELive%20like%20a%20Maratha%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarlekar%20and%20Shetye%20have%20been%20urban%20planners%20for%20two%20decades%20now%2C%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20sustainable%20architecture.%20Chavni%20imbues%20these%20concepts%20in%20the%20form%20of%20its%20mini%20carts%2C%20seven%20royal%20tents%2C%20five%20luxury%20carts%2C%20and%20a%20two-bedroom%20classic%20suite%20(%3Cem%3Ewada%3C%2Fem%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20the%20stays%20are%20designed%20on%20the%20concept%20of%20%E2%80%98being%20in%20transit%E2%80%99.%20Tribes%20throughout%20history%20have%20always%20moved%20from%20one%20place%20to%20another%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Karlekar.%20It%20was%20this%20rhythm%20of%20movement%2C%20she%20says%2C%20that%20separated%20the%20opulent%20Moghuls%20from%20the%20simpler%20Marathas.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20latter%20only%20carried%20as%20much%20as%20they%20required%20and%20depended%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F279565%2Ftraditional-indian-food-for-summer-roohafza-sherbet-kokum-sattu-buy-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20local%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20grain%2C%20and%20vegetables%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20their%20needs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20same%20ethos%20is%20championed%20at%20Chavni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3C